NK004(nga)001:1571: rnams gang 'grub rtse gcig tu bzlas shing /
NK004(nga)001:1572: mthar mchod bstod spyi khyab mdor bsdus dang /
NK004(nga)001:1574: lhar 'od du zhu ba las gzungs dang rdzas la
NK004(nga)001:1575: thim pas phyi nang gi nyes pa thams cad zhi
NK004(nga)001:1576: zhing snod bcud kyi dpal phun sum tshogs pa bskyed
NK004(nga)001:1577: pa'i gter chen po'i bum pa bzang por gyur cig
NK004(nga)001:1578: / ces brtan bzhugs dang shis brjod rgyas par bya /
NK004(nga)001:1579: de nas sa dgra yod phyogs sogs gang du sbas pa'i sar lag tshag dam par gzhug /
NK004(nga)001:1580: grub na cho ga tshar gcig bskyar /
NK004(nga)001:1581: ma grub kyang brtan bzhugs smon lam bkra shis brjod pa sogs byas pas kyang grub bo //
NK004(nga)001:1582: lnga pa dzam gter bum sgrub ni /
NK004(nga)001:1584: bum pa rin po che dang rdza bum gang 'byor
NK004(nga)001:1585: log la rtags brgyad sogs ri mo bris pa'i nang
NK004(nga)001:1586: du rgya bod kyi zhing sa bzang po'i sa sna
NK004(nga)001:1589: phyug po g.yang can gyi nor sna /
NK004(nga)001:1591: rta phyug gi spu sna tshogs sogs phyug rgyun ma chad pa'i rdzas ci mang /
NK004(nga)001:1592: dngos grub gyi rdzas sna tshogs /
NK004(nga)001:1593: sman sna sogs bum rdzas rnams la grib can dang
NK004(nga)001:1594: mi gtsang ba med par phyi nang kun la lag
NK004(nga)001:1596: gtso bo a ru ra gser mdog gcig la dar dmar log la /
NK004(nga)001:1598: dzam+b+ha la dza len t+r+aa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1599: zhes gser gyi bris la dril /
NK004(nga)001:1600: de phyir nor rgyun ma'i gzungs /
NK004(nga)001:1601: ba su d+ha ri ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1602: zhes dar dkar la bris pas dril te bcug pa'am /
NK004(nga)001:1603: min kyang gzungs gnyis phreng gcig byas te srog shing
NK004(nga)001:1604: la dril te na bza' ser po gsol nas gzhug
NK004(nga)001:1605: go / gzungs kyi mjug tu 'dod gsol /
NK004(nga)001:1607: pun+d+yee sid+d+hi h'uh d+ha na me d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1609: rdzas dang bca' bkod rnams grub nas /
NK004(nga)001:1610: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'gram mam mdun du bum pa rnams bshams /
NK004(nga)001:1611: bum pa'i mdun zangs gzhong lta bu'i nang dzam gtor dang /
NK004(nga)001:1613: sgrub pa po sha chang sogs kyi dri ma med
NK004(nga)001:1614: pa gtsang sbra la gnas pas bdag bskyed bsnyen bstod
NK004(nga)001:1615: bcas tshar nas / bum gter la bsang chu bran zhing /
NK004(nga)001:1617: stong pa'i ngang las dgos 'dod dpal gyi gsang gter
NK004(nga)001:1618: chen po bum pa chen po mdzes shing yid du
NK004(nga)001:1619: 'ong ba blta na sdug pa'i nang du snang srid
NK004(nga)001:1620: rab 'byams kyi 'dod dgu'i dpal dang gzi brjid stobs
NK004(nga)001:1621: dang mnga' thang las grub pa'i yo byad thams cad
NK004(nga)001:1622: ma tshang ba med cing tshangs shing yid du 'ong
NK004(nga)001:1623: ba'i tshang chen gyi bskal ba 'bum phrag du mar
NK004(nga)001:1624: brdal ba'i dus su yang zad mi shes pa'i yon
NK004(nga)001:1625: tan gyi dpal thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i rang
NK004(nga)001:1628: khyad par sngags drug phyag drug bdun nam gsum brjod /
NK004(nga)001:1629: na mo bdag gi bsam pa'i stobs sogs brjod /
NK004(nga)001:1630: mdun du rin po che'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus
NK004(nga)001:1631: su pam las pad zla'i steng du dzam ser po
NK004(nga)001:1632: las / dzam b+ha la ser po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK004(nga)001:1633: phyag g.yas pas b+ai dza p+au ra dang /
NK004(nga)001:1634: g.yon rin po che skyug pa'i ne'u le 'dzin pa /
NK004(nga)001:1635: dar dang rin po che ut+pala yi phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK004(nga)001:1636: zhabs rol pa'i stobs kyis dung dang bum pa rin po che'i gter gnon par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1639: rgyal ba rnams kyi phrin las kyis //
NK004(nga)001:1640: 'gro ba'i dbul ba sel mdzad pa'i //
NK004(nga)001:1641: gzhan don sems bskyed dzam b+ha la //
NK004(nga)001:1643: dzam b+ha la badz+ra sa ma ya dza dzah bzhugs gsol phyag mchod ni /
NK004(nga)001:1645: rgyal bas basngagasa pa'i bsod nams stobs kyi nor //
NK004(nga)001:1646: sems bskyed dad pa'i rten la bzhugs su gsol //
NK004(nga)001:1647: rgyal ba'i rnam 'phrul gnod sbyin yon tan la //
NK004(nga)001:1648: nges 'byung dad pa'i phyag gi mchod pa che //
NK004(nga)001:1652: mi bzad gter la mnga' mdzad cing //
NK004(nga)001:1653: 'dod pa'i dngos grub stsol mdzad pa'i //
NK004(nga)001:1654: gnod sbyin yongs kyi ded dpon mchog /
NK004(nga)001:1658: gtso bo'i thugs ka'i 'od zer shin tu rnon pos
NK004(nga)001:1659: dzam yig sngags phreng dang bcas pa bskul bas srid
NK004(nga)001:1660: pa'i laspyongasa da char du babs pas yul ljongs dang
NK004(nga)001:1661: gnas khang gang bar bsam mo //
NK004(nga)001:1662: dzam+b+ha la dza len+t+ra ye a yudz+ny+aa na pun+d+ye sid+d+hi h'uh d+ha na me d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1664: mthar chu sbyin chab gtor ltar gtong gsung pas /
NK004(nga)001:1665: mdun du rin chen gdan steng du //
NK004(nga)001:1666: dzam las rin chen 'bar ba la //
NK004(nga)001:1667: nor lha ser po 'dzum bag can //
NK004(nga)001:1668: zhal gcig phyag gnyis zhi ba'i sku //
NK004(nga)001:1669: sems dpa'i dkyil krung lcang lo 'khyil //
NK004(nga)001:1670: phyag g.yas mchod sbyin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK004(nga)001:1671: g.yon pa'i ne'u le'i rkyal pa bsnam //
NK004(nga)001:1676: gsang ba'i gnod sbyin nor gyi bdag gter bdag dzam lha dgongs su gsol /
NK004(nga)001:1677: bdag gi mchod yon chu sbyin bzhes /
NK004(nga)001:1678: tshe dang longs spyod dngos grub stsol /
NK004(nga)001:1685: bum pa'i lha 'od du zhu ba las rdzas dang
NK004(nga)001:1686: gzungs la thim pas srid pa'i dpal 'byor longs spyod
NK004(nga)001:1687: char ltar 'bebs pa'i gter chen po'i bum pa bzang
NK004(nga)001:1688: por gyur / bstan bzhugs dang shis brjod rgyas par bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:1689: drug pa gnod sbyin 'khor lo'iraba gnas dang sgrub pa ni /
NK004(nga)001:1690: rab tu ma gnas pa la bsgrub pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:1691: ma bsgrub par rab gnas byas pa tsam gyis rten gyi nang du gzhug mi rung bar gsungs pas /
NK004(nga)001:1692: rab gnas zhabs drung pad phrin pas gsungs ltar na /
NK004(nga)001:1693: gnod sbyin 'khor lo bris pa'am spar la btab pa sogs skabs thob tshon gyi bkra bar byas la /
NK004(nga)001:1694: gur gum dang g+hi wam sogs kyis byug ste /
NK004(nga)001:1695: rdo rje slob dpon byang du blta ba'i mdun du
NK004(nga)001:1696: zangs gzhongs sogs snod gtsang ma'i steng du rin po
NK004(nga)001:1697: che sna tshogs bkram pa'i dbus su 'khor lo gnyis
NK004(nga)001:1698: kha bye bas zhal rang la phyogs par bshams pa'i
NK004(nga)001:1699: mdun du sbyang chas rnams dang /
NK004(nga)001:1701: mchod yon sngon 'gro'i mchod pa bshams /
NK004(nga)001:1703: bla med kyi lha gang rung gi bdag bskyed kyi
NK004(nga)001:1704: rnal 'byor tshul bzhin bsgom pa sngon du song bas
NK004(nga)001:1705: dkyil 'khor bsdu / gtso bo'i nga rgyal gyi sbyang ba gsum dang /
NK004(nga)001:1706: bum pa'i chus tshig bcad ci rigs kyis khrus gsol /
NK004(nga)001:1707: 'khor lo bsang sbyang mi dmigs te /
NK004(nga)001:1708: stong pa'i ngang las rma byas btegs pa'i rin po
NK004(nga)001:1709: che'i khri pad+ma dang zla ba'i steng du hrihdang pad+ma
NK004(nga)001:1710: las 'od dpag med sku mdog dmar po mnyam bzhag
NK004(nga)001:1711: gi phyag rgya can dar gyi stod g.yog dang sham
NK004(nga)001:1712: thabs can rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa rdo
NK004(nga)001:1713: rje'i dkyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'i dpral bar /
NK004(nga)001:1715: h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas 'og min dang rang
NK004(nga)001:1716: bzhin gyi gnas nas sangs rgyas thams cad 'od dpag
NK004(nga)001:1717: med kyi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes spyan
NK004(nga)001:1718: drangs / dzahmh'u bam hohs pa ye shes pa bstim pas /
NK004(nga)001:1719: slar yang thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas 'og
NK004(nga)001:1720: min nas dbang gi lha rigs lnga 'khor dang bcas
NK004(nga)001:1722: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis 'di la dbang bskur du gsol /
NK004(nga)001:1728: chu'i lhag ma yar lud pa las rang 'dra'i rigs bdag gis dbur brgyan par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1732: stong pa'i ngang las mchod rdzas rnams dwangs shing thog
NK004(nga)001:1733: pa med pa zag pa med pa bde ba khyad
NK004(nga)001:1734: par can skyed pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par gyur
NK004(nga)001:1736: a mi ta b+ha wa h+r+ai /
NK004(nga)001:1739: gan+d+he ra ni sa rol mo phul /
NK004(nga)001:1741: 'dod chags rdo rje chos kyi sku /
NK004(nga)001:1742: kun rtogs ye shes ngo bo nyid /
NK004(nga)001:1743: ting 'dzin chen po'i phyag rgya can /
NK004(nga)001:1744: phyag 'tshal snang ba mtha' yas la /
NK004(nga)001:1746: 'od dpag med zhu ba las byung ba'i 'khor lo gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1748: 'khor lo la bkod pa'i sngags rnams brgya rtsa re
NK004(nga)001:1749: dang rten 'brel snying po brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas
NK004(nga)001:1750: brtan par bya / me tog 'thor zhing /
NK004(nga)001:1751: su pra tish+tha mang du brjod /
NK004(nga)001:1752: bdag dang sbyin pa'i bdag po'i dpal 'byor longs spyod mnga' thang thams cad rgyas par mdzad du gsol /
NK004(nga)001:1755: de ltar 'khor lo bsgrub par rab gnas tsam gyis mi 'thus par gsungs pas /
NK004(nga)001:1756: kun mkhyen lnga pa'i gsung bzhin sgrub chog mdor bsdus ni /
NK004(nga)001:1757: rab gnas zin pa'i 'khor lo mar dang sbrang rtsi
NK004(nga)001:1758: ka ra bsres pa gur gum dang dri bzang po
NK004(nga)001:1759: sbyar bas pad 'dab rnams kyis mtshams su brlan te
NK004(nga)001:1760: pho 'khor steng dang mo 'khor 'og tu byas te
NK004(nga)001:1761: 'grigs par sbyar ba dang dar ram ras skud ser
NK004(nga)001:1762: pos 'khor lo mi mngon par dkri /
NK004(nga)001:1763: skud pa'i lhag ma pho 'khor steng du mdud cog khug byas pa la gzung /
NK004(nga)001:1766: sgrub pa po dge slong gtsang ma dbang thob pa grangs ci rigs pas /
NK004(nga)001:1767: gnas dben par phyag dar byas la sgrub pa po
NK004(nga)001:1768: rnams kha 'jig rten pa'i byang du bstan pa'i mdun
NK004(nga)001:1769: khru do pa'i man+dala gru bzhi pa'i phyi rol sor
NK004(nga)001:1770: brgyad pa'i cha la gru bzhir bcad la re kha
NK004(nga)001:1771: dkar po nyis rim gyis bcad pa'i phyi nang thams
NK004(nga)001:1772: cad tshon ser pos bkang ba'am /
NK004(nga)001:1773: yang na stegs bu dar ser po'i bkab pa'i steng
NK004(nga)001:1774: zangs gzhong 'bru dang rin po che gos dar sman
NK004(nga)001:1775: sna tshogs kyis bkang ba'i dbus su /
NK004(nga)001:1776: dar ser po'i steng 'khor lo 'jig rten pa'i lhor bltas te bzhag /
NK004(nga)001:1777: 'khor lo mang du yod na brtsegs mar bzhag pa'i steng gi mdud cog la gzung thag gdags /
NK004(nga)001:1778: steng du dar ser po'i gur phub pa'am dgab /
NK004(nga)001:1779: spro na phyogs mtshams thams cad du dar ser po'i
NK004(nga)001:1780: rgyal mtshan 'dzug mthar chu gnyis nyer spyod lnga g.yas
NK004(nga)001:1781: skor du bshams / sha chang ma 'dres pa'i dkar gsum mngar gsum sogs kha zas shing thog /
NK004(nga)001:1782: 'bru sman ja sogs bza' btung mang pos brgyan pa'i dkar gtor gcig bshams /
NK004(nga)001:1783: rang gi mdun rdor dril me tog sogs kyang 'du bya /
NK004(nga)001:1784: khrus dang gtsang sbra rdor skyil dkar sogs kyi spyod
NK004(nga)001:1785: lam dang bcas te lpags rigs min pa'i stan la
NK004(nga)001:1787: 'khor lo rnams las sngags kyis bsang /
NK004(nga)001:1789: stong pa'i ngang las rdo rje'i sa gzhi rwa ba
NK004(nga)001:1790: d+r+wa ba gur bla bre me ri dang bcas pa'i
NK004(nga)001:1791: nang du sna tshogs pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lte
NK004(nga)001:1792: ba dang phyogs mtshams rnams su /
NK004(nga)001:1793: bam dang dzam yongs su gyur pa las /
NK004(nga)001:1794: gnod sbyin yab yum rnams kyi sku yongs su rdzogs
NK004(nga)001:1795: par gyur pa'i gtso 'khor thams cad sku mdog gser
NK004(nga)001:1796: btso ma lta bu zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas thams
NK004(nga)001:1797: cad bi dza p+au ra dang /
NK004(nga)001:1798: yab rnams kyi g.yon pas ne'u le dang /
NK004(nga)001:1799: yum rnams kyi g.yon pas 'bras kyi snye ma 'dzin pa /
NK004(nga)001:1800: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyi sa brgyan pa /
NK004(nga)001:1801: zhabs skyil krung phyed pas bzhugs pa'i zhabs 'og nas pad+ma'i gdong gis gter mnan pa /
NK004(nga)001:1802: lha mo rnams bud med sgyu ma'i nga rgyal gyis
NK004(nga)001:1803: 'gying bar gyur pa'i gtso 'khor thams cad kyis spyi
NK004(nga)001:1804: bor / mgrin par +aah thugs kar h'u gis mtshan par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1805: thugs kar h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas rang bzhin
NK004(nga)001:1806: gyis gnas nas sgom pa dang 'dra ba'i ye shes
NK004(nga)001:1807: pa dbang lha dang bcas spyan drangs /
NK004(nga)001:1808: dzahmh'u bam hoh gnyis su med par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1809: dbang lhas dbang bskur rin 'byung gis dbu rgyan par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1813: stong pa'i ngang las las rin po che'i snod yangs
NK004(nga)001:1814: shing rgya che ba rnams kyi nang du 'od du
NK004(nga)001:1815: zhu ba las byung ba'i mchod yon /
NK004(nga)001:1818: rol mo rnams dwangs shing thog pa med pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1821: ba su d+ha ra ni sa pa ri wa ra ar+g+ham nas /
NK004(nga)001:1823: nor gyi dbang phyug sogs kyis bstod /
NK004(nga)001:1826: lha rnams kyi thugs kar zla gdan la bam yig
NK004(nga)001:1827: dang dzam yig gi mthar rang rang gi sngags phreng
NK004(nga)001:1828: gi bskor ba las 'od zer 'phros srid zhi'i dpal
NK004(nga)001:1829: 'byor thams cad spyan drangs te 'od du zhu nas
NK004(nga)001:1830: sbyin bdag dang 'khor lo la thims te dbul phongs
NK004(nga)001:1831: zhi zhing dpal 'byor phun sum tshogs par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1832: ba su d+ha ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1834: da na da ye ba su d+aa na ye ad+ya
NK004(nga)001:1835: ye su b+ha dra ye gub+ta ye dee byee s+w+aa
NK004(nga)001:1836: h+aa / swa ra swa t+yee s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1837: dzam b+ha la dza len+t+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1838: ma ni b+ha dra ya pra rna b+ha dra ya
NK004(nga)001:1839: d+ha na d+aa ya be sh+ra ma na ya ka
NK004(nga)001:1841: tsi pi ku n+da li mu khen+t+ra ya tsa reen+t+ra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1843: rjes yig brgyas kha bskong ngo //
NK004(nga)001:1847: swa b+h+aa was sbyangs byas te /
NK004(nga)001:1848: stong pa'i ngang las las rin po che'i snod yangs
NK004(nga)001:1849: shing rgya che ba'i nang du 'od du zhu ba
NK004(nga)001:1850: las lha rdzas las grub pa'i gtor ma dwangs shing
NK004(nga)001:1851: thog pa med pa zag pa med pa'i ye shes
NK004(nga)001:1852: kyi bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK004(nga)001:1855: gnod sbyin yab yum gyi ljags h'u las skyes pa'i
NK004(nga)001:1856: rdo rje rtse gcig pa dkar po 'od kyi sbu
NK004(nga)001:1857: gus gtor ma'i bcud drangs te gsol bar bsam /
NK004(nga)001:1858: ba su d+ha ri ni sa p+aa ri wa ra
NK004(nga)001:1859: e dam b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa
NK004(nga)001:1860: hi / zhes gsum mam bdun gyis 'bul /
NK004(nga)001:1862: 'phags ma nor rgyun ma yab yum gtso 'khor rnams
NK004(nga)001:1863: sgrub gzhi 'di la brten par bzhugs nas rten la
NK004(nga)001:1864: mchod pa dang / sbyin bdag dang bdag sogs sems
NK004(nga)001:1865: can thams cad la dpal 'byor rgya chen po rgyun
NK004(nga)001:1866: mi 'chad du 'byung bar mdzad du gsol /
NK004(nga)001:1868: ye shes pa 'od du zhu nas 'khor lo'i rnam par gyur par bsam /
NK004(nga)001:1869: ye d+har gyis rab tu gnas par bya zhing /
NK004(nga)001:1871: su pra tish+thasa brtan par byas te /
NK004(nga)001:1872: bkra shis rgyas par brjod par bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:1874: blo gros mtha' yas kyis gsung ltar te /
NK004(nga)001:1875: mchod rten du 'bul rgyu'i gzungs rnams thams cad dang /
NK004(nga)001:1876: s+aats+tsha'i gzungs dang bum gter sogs thams cad la ma
NK004(nga)001:1877: bsgril bar sbyong khrus rab gnas byas te bsgril zin
NK004(nga)001:1878: pa dang na bza' ser po gsol te dkyil 'khor
NK004(nga)001:1879: du bshams / rtsa ba'i bdag bskyed bzlas pa bsdu ldang grub pa na /
NK004(nga)001:1881: mdun gyi mchod pa rnams bsang sbyangs byin rlabs spyi ltar bya /
NK004(nga)001:1882: de nas gzungs gzhug rnams bsang sbyang /
NK004(nga)001:1883: stong pa'i ngang las seng ges btegs pa'i khri pad+ma
NK004(nga)001:1884: nyi zla'i steng du bde gshegs rigs kyi snying po
NK004(nga)001:1885: nye snying gsang sngags rigs sngags thams cad kyi sngags
NK004(nga)001:1886: phreng dkar po / glang pos btegs pa'i khri pad+ma
NK004(nga)001:1887: nyi zla'i steng du rdo rje rigs kyi snying po
NK004(nga)001:1888: nye snying gsang sngags rigs sngags gzungs sngags thams cad
NK004(nga)001:1890: rta mchog gis btegs pa'i khri pad+ma nyi zla'i steng
NK004(nga)001:1891: du rin chen rigs kyi snying po nye snying gsang
NK004(nga)001:1892: sngags rigs sngags thams cad kyi snying po sngags phreng
NK004(nga)001:1893: ser po / rma byas btegs pa'i khri pad+ma nyi
NK004(nga)001:1894: zla'i steng du pad+ma rigs kyi snying po nye snying
NK004(nga)001:1895: gsang sngags rigs sngags gzungs sngags thams cad sngags phreng
NK004(nga)001:1896: ser po / dmar po / mkha' lding gis btegs
NK004(nga)001:1897: pa'i khri pad+ma nyi zla'i steng du las kyi rigs
NK004(nga)001:1898: kyi snying po nye snying gsang sngags rigs sngags gzungs
NK004(nga)001:1899: sngags thams cad sngags phreng ljang gu /
NK004(nga)001:1900: thams cad kyang rang mdog gi 'od zer 'bar zhing
NK004(nga)001:1901: rang sgra sgrogs bzhin pa las 'od zer dpag tu
NK004(nga)001:1902: med pa 'phros / mkha' khyab tu bzhugs pa'i mchog
NK004(nga)001:1903: gsum rtsa gsum chos skyong srung ma dang bcas pa'i
NK004(nga)001:1904: med pa 'phros / thugs rgyud bskul / de dag
NK004(nga)001:1905: gi gnas gsum las gsang ba gsum gyi byin brlabs
NK004(nga)001:1906: med pa 'phros / thugs rgyud bskul / dang /
NK004(nga)001:1907: khyad par gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu'i chos sgo
NK004(nga)001:1908: brgyad khri bzhi stong gi bcud thams cad so so'i
NK004(nga)001:1909: snying po nye snying sngags phreng kha dogs sna tshogs
NK004(nga)001:1910: pa'i tshul nam mkha' gang ba tsam du byon nas
NK004(nga)001:1911: dam tshig pa'i yig 'bru rnams la thim pas gzi
NK004(nga)001:1914: nang gzhug gang yod kyi sngags rnams ji ltar rigs pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:1918: h'u h+r+aihb+hu kham badz+ri b+ha wa dri d+ha tish+tha b+b+hu kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:1921: a tsin+d+ya b+hu ta r+au pi ni /
NK004(nga)001:1927: sogs shwa lo ka gsum dang /
NK004(nga)001:1929: de dag basngagasa pa dang bstod par 'os pas bstod /
NK004(nga)001:1934: sogs kyis bkra shis rgyas pa brjod pas grub pa yin no //
NK004(nga)001:1935: brgyad pa rab gnas me tog sgrub pa ni /
NK004(nga)001:1936: smin gling gter chen gsung ltar la /
NK004(nga)001:1937: rin po che'i gzhong pa me tog gis bkang ba'i
NK004(nga)001:1938: dbus su many+dza'i steng du gzungs bum dri'i chus bkang
NK004(nga)001:1939: ba'i khar gser dngul lta bu'i me long la tsan+dana
NK004(nga)001:1940: dkar po / gur gum gi wam rnams 'o ma
NK004(nga)001:1941: dang sbyar nas rten snying tshar bdun bris steng dang
NK004(nga)001:1942: dkar po / s+w+aa h+aa / 'og tu yod par byas nas yig phreng ltar bri ba yin /
NK004(nga)001:1943: tshar gcig bri kyang mdor bsdus chog /
NK004(nga)001:1946: mdun du dri chu'i dung zhal yang bzhag /
NK004(nga)001:1947: thog mar yi dam gang rung gi bdag bskyed sngon du 'gro bas /
NK004(nga)001:1950: stong pa'i ngang las rin po che'i bum pa mtshan
NK004(nga)001:1951: nyid thams cad rdzogs pa'i steng du zla ba la
NK004(nga)001:1952: gnas pa'i rten 'brel snying po'i sngags phreng 'od zer
NK004(nga)001:1953: gyi phung po 'bar bas 'khor bcas kyi bdud rtsi
NK004(nga)001:1954: thams cad bsdus nas 'od du zhu ba bum chu
NK004(nga)001:1955: dang ro gcig tu 'dres par bsam shing /
NK004(nga)001:1958: khri phrag tsam res byin gyis brlab /
NK004(nga)001:1959: mthar dung zhal gyi chus me long gi yig ge rnams gzungs bum du sbyang /
NK004(nga)001:1960: de nas bum chus me tog la khyad par bris te /
NK004(nga)001:1961: me tog rnams re re nas rten 'brel snying po'i
NK004(nga)001:1962: yig 'bru gser 'od 'bar ba re'i rang bzhin gyur
NK004(nga)001:1963: par bsam / shis brjod rgyas par bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:1964: rab gnas me tog 'di ni rten bzhugs bkra shis kyi skabs 'thor rgyu dang /
NK004(nga)001:1965: s+aats+tsha'i nang du gzungs gzhug rgyu yin cing /
NK004(nga)001:1966: dri med rnam gnyis kyi phan yon ni gzungs 'di la dgongs pa yin pa las /
NK004(nga)001:1967: gzhan s+aats+tsha gzung gzhug med pa rnams la rab gnas
NK004(nga)001:1968: me tog 'di phul na gzungs kyis dod chog pa
NK004(nga)001:1969: lha gcig jo bo'i phyag bzhes las shes pas /
NK004(nga)001:1970: sbyin bdag rnams kyis s+aats+tsha'i gzungs gzhug tu yin zer nas /
NK004(nga)001:1971: 'bru zhal phu ru khyer 'ong dus bla ma rnams
NK004(nga)001:1972: nas khung med kyi sngags nyob mang po las rten
NK004(nga)001:1973: snying tshar cha shas re gsungs na bka' drin che'o
NK004(nga)001:1974: // de ltar ji skad bshad pa thams cad las /
NK004(nga)001:1977: nyes sel rnams ni 'og gi ma sa'i nang du
NK004(nga)001:1978: rdo sgrom sogs lag tshag dam por sba ba dang
NK004(nga)001:1979: / de steng dbus drang thad dkyil 'khor gyi 'og
NK004(nga)001:1980: tu rdo cig bang sgrom gang bde byas pa'i nang
NK004(nga)001:1981: du gnod sbyin nor lha'i pho brang mtshon byed phyogs
NK004(nga)001:1982: bzhi dbus lngar nor bum 'am de min gang 'dzom
NK004(nga)001:1983: / bya / khyad par dbus stegs kyi steng gnod
NK004(nga)001:1984: sbyin 'khor lo ma grub pa rab gnas tsam gyi
NK004(nga)001:1985: mi 'thus pas tshul bzhin sgrub pa skud pa ser
NK004(nga)001:1986: po dang na bza' ser pos dkris pa /
NK004(nga)001:1987: gzhug snod dkar yol bkra shis rtags brgyad dam /
NK004(nga)001:1988: phor ba lta bu tshon dmar ser gyi byug pa'i
NK004(nga)001:1989: nang du zhun mar dang sbrang rtsi bsres pa'i dang
NK004(nga)001:1991: de steng 'khor lo dbu zhabs ma log par leb
NK004(nga)001:1992: mor pho steng mo 'og gtso bo'i dbu nub bstan
NK004(nga)001:1993: du bzhag go / 'di bzhag lugs mang po yod kyang 'di'i 'thus /
NK004(nga)001:1994: de yi steng mar dang sbrang rtsis kha bkang nas /
NK004(nga)001:1995: dar dmar ser gyis dril te /
NK004(nga)001:1996: skud pa ser pos dkris la bzhag go /
NK004(nga)001:1997: de'i dbus su mdo rgyud nas byung ba'i bkra shis skor dang /
NK004(nga)001:1998: g.yas su chos skyong srung ma'i sngags /
NK004(nga)001:1999: g.yon du dpal mgon bdun cu /
NK004(nga)001:2000: rgyab tu gnod sbyin nor lha phyogs skyongs rgyal chen /
NK004(nga)001:2001: gza' rgyu skar lha klu sa bdag mthu bo che rnams kyi sngags dang /
NK004(nga)001:2002: 'dod gsol gyi shog dril rnams bzhag /
NK004(nga)001:2003: phyogs mtshams thams cad du bra sran sogs 'bru nag ma yin pa'i 'bru sna tshogs /
NK004(nga)001:2004: sha ma gtogs ja mar tsha sogs dang /
NK004(nga)001:2006: dug rigs med pa'i sman sna /
NK004(nga)001:2007: me tog sna tshogs mgo snam dang 'phrug sogs 'bu chags pa'i rigs cher med pa /
NK004(nga)001:2008: dar ras gos chen gang yod /
NK004(nga)001:2009: 'bru sna sogs ras ser po'i khug mar blug /
NK004(nga)001:2011: dkar po gur gum dang yung ba sin+d+hu ra lta bus kha dogs ser po byed pa ma gtogs /
NK004(nga)001:2012: rgyas pa'i las yin pas snod dkar po sngo nag ljang sogs su blug srol med /
NK004(nga)001:2013: 'bru rnams rdo rdul sogs lhad med dang /
NK004(nga)001:2014: bkru bar 'os pa rnams bkrus te skam bcol /
NK004(nga)001:2015: mi 'os pa rnams bsang bdug bya ba sogs gtsang sbra gal che /
NK004(nga)001:2016: de ltar gnod sbyin bang mdzod du 'bul 'os thams cad la /
NK004(nga)001:2017: sbyong khrus dang sgrub pa sngar bshad pa bzhin bya /
NK004(nga)001:2018: 'bru sogs kyi bang sgrom ma kheng na shug phye sogs /
NK004(nga)001:2019: bzang shing gi phye mas legs par bkang bar bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2020: de ltar nor bum sogs bum gter skor ha cang mang zhing gtso bor bya ba ni /
NK004(nga)001:2021: rgyal bas gsung ba'i dam chos rin po che g.yas chung su bzhag nas /
NK004(nga)001:2022: 'jig rten pa'i chos skyong nor lha'i rten gtor gal
NK004(nga)001:2023: chen bya ba ni blun po mkhas 'dod can gyi
NK004(nga)001:2024: rnam thar yin pas chos spyan ldan pa rnams kyis
NK004(nga)001:2025: dbye bsal shes par bya dgos kyang /
NK004(nga)001:2026: snyigs ma'i dus 'dir sa'i bcud nyams skye 'gro'i g.yang
NK004(nga)001:2027: nyams snod bcud rgud pas gdung ba'i gnas skabs 'dir
NK004(nga)001:2028: / dam pa gong ma'i gsung bzhin rang rang gi
NK004(nga)001:2029: skab thos su bsgrub te phul na snod bcud kyi
NK004(nga)001:2030: rgud pa la phan yang srid snyams te mdor bsdus
NK004(nga)001:2031: te bris pa yin cing rgyas pa rang phyogs kyi
NK004(nga)001:2032: yig cha las shes par bya zhing /
NK004(nga)001:2033: mdor na sa bum klu bum nyes sel bum pa
NK004(nga)001:2034: nor bum gnod sbyin 'khor lo sogs ni ma byas
NK004(nga)001:2035: kyang chad pa'i skyon med cing yan lag 'di dag
NK004(nga)001:2036: ha cang rgyas na lo mas 'bras bu sgrib pa'i
NK004(nga)001:2037: dpe bzhin yin pas skabs su gang dgos zhib dpyad
NK004(nga)001:2039: dngos gzhi dri med rnam gnyis kyi mchod pa nyer
NK004(nga)001:2040: spyod sogs gal chung du mi mdzad pa thugs la
NK004(nga)001:2042: gnyis pa dri med rnam gnyis kyi yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la /
NK004(nga)001:2043: thun mong gi yan lag dang /
NK004(nga)001:2045: dang po la char pa gcod pa /
NK004(nga)001:2047: sa sgrub dkyil 'khor dang mchod pa'i dbye bsdu /
NK004(nga)001:2048: cho ga rgyas bsdus kyi gtong tshul te bzhi'o //
NK004(nga)001:2050: gnub kyi gong khug sro ma can gyi shog dril gyi nang tshan ltar na /
NK004(nga)001:2051: rang nyid skad cig gi bya khyung dmar po /
NK004(nga)001:2052: sgro gshog mchu dang bcas pa thams cad me 'bar
NK004(nga)001:2053: bas kha char gtong ba'i klu sbrul gyi rnam pa
NK004(nga)001:2054: gsal ba tshig cing nyam thag tu gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2055: me de yang stong gsum gang bar bskyed la /
NK004(nga)001:2056: n+aa ga r+aa tsa char chod /
NK004(nga)001:2057: nu g+aa r+aa tsa char chod /
NK004(nga)001:2059: rdzas la rtsam pa snying ba dang /
NK004(nga)001:2060: tsha bsres te mer bsreg go //
NK004(nga)001:2066: tho rang bya kha ta'i skad ma grags gong bzlas
NK004(nga)001:2067: pa'i rdzas me thal 'jam po la bsregs shing dud
NK004(nga)001:2068: pa btang / nam mkha' la phu rgyags /
NK004(nga)001:2069: rang gi mgo steng dang kha char gar babs sa ru bskyed rim gsal sngags phu 'debs so //
NK004(nga)001:2070: dang po kha char gcod pa'i tshe /
NK004(nga)001:2071: bsang dang gser skyems bya zhing bden pa brjod /
NK004(nga)001:2072: des ma chod na zhi rdzas la sngags btab cing mer bsregs /
NK004(nga)001:2073: des ma chod na drag rdzas la bya /
NK004(nga)001:2074: des ma chod na gnam 'khor sa 'khor sogs gsung kyang ma bris so //
NK004(nga)001:2075: de dag gi skabs thams cad du rang nyid khyung gi bskyed rim ma chags par bsgom /
NK004(nga)001:2076: spyir sngags pa khyung gi bsnyen tshad rtag thon dgos gsung pas /
NK004(nga)001:2077: ci yang ma yin pas sngags cha shas re bton
NK004(nga)001:2078: nas ma chod pa na gdam ngag la log lta
NK004(nga)001:2080: thams cad rang phyogs nas lan pa yin pa shes par gyis /
NK004(nga)001:2081: rjes bsang dang gser skyem klu gtor sogs la 'bad pa gal che'o //
NK004(nga)001:2082: 'di ni kho bo'i snga phyi lan mang por mchod
NK004(nga)001:2083: rten bzhengs pa dang s+aats+tsha gdabs pa'i tshe char chu
NK004(nga)001:2085: s+aats+tsha mang po 'o brgyal la gtug pa sogs ci
NK004(nga)001:2086: bya gtol med de byung bas 'di bris pa yin
NK004(nga)001:2087: te / gzhan lo thog sogs la mi gnod ba'i dus yin na ma gtogs /
NK004(nga)001:2088: gzhan gnod kyi rgyur 'gyur na ni nam yang mi bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2089: gnyis pa s+aats+tsha gdabs pa'i rim pa ni /
NK004(nga)001:2090: rdo rje slob dpon bsnyen pa sogs sngon du song ba'i gang zag gis /
NK004(nga)001:2091: dang po s+aats+tsha'i rgyu sa gang nas len pa'i gzhir dkar gtor dang gser skyem bshams /
NK004(nga)001:2092: 'og gi nyer mkho rnams 'du byas la /
NK004(nga)001:2093: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems bskyed la /
NK004(nga)001:2095: sangs rgyas chos dang sogs sems can thams cad sogs tshad med bzhi bsgom zhing /
NK004(nga)001:2096: rang nyid rdo rje 'dzin pa'i skur gsal ba'i thugs
NK004(nga)001:2097: ka'i 'od kyis gnas dang gzhi'i bdag po 'khor dang
NK004(nga)001:2098: bcas pa spyan drangs gtor ma phul bas dgyes par
NK004(nga)001:2099: gyur / swa b+h+aa wa sogs 'bul tshig rgyas bsdus ci 'grub dang /
NK004(nga)001:2100: gang dag 'dir gnas lha dang klu /
NK004(nga)001:2101: gnod sbyin srin po'am gzhan dag la /
NK004(nga)001:2102: mchod rten don du sa phyogs 'di /
NK004(nga)001:2103: bdag zhu khyed kyis rtsal du gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2105: rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyi las ci bde bar byos shig ces gnang ba byin par bsam mo //
NK004(nga)001:2106: de nas tshon skud lnga bsgril gyi skud pas sa
NK004(nga)001:2107: ci tsam dgos pa'i rgya khyon gyi mthar gru bzhir
NK004(nga)001:2108: bcad la / badz+ra s+au tra h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2110: sa la gnas pa'i gdon bgegs bsam sbyor ngan pa
NK004(nga)001:2111: mchod rten dang dge ba'i las la bar du gcod
NK004(nga)001:2112: pa thams cad rdo rje'i d+r+wa bas mtshams bcad gzhi
NK004(nga)001:2113: de nyid rin po che sna tshogs pa'i rang bzhin
NK004(nga)001:2114: du gyur / de nas seng lding gi phur bu
NK004(nga)001:2115: sor brgyad pa lnga dbus dang thig gi grwa bzhir
NK004(nga)001:2116: du gyur / gdabs / gcig las ma 'byor na 'debs tshul byas la mthar dbus su gdabs te /
NK004(nga)001:2117: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba dush+tana h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2119: sa ci tsam blang dgos pa blang la /
NK004(nga)001:2120: blang zin gyi bar du thig skud dang phur bu mi bsdu'o //
NK004(nga)001:2121: de nas til dang yungs dkar la /
NK004(nga)001:2122: a mri te h+aa na ha na h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2124: bgegs thams cad tshar gcad de /
NK004(nga)001:2125: sa'i phyogs de bzhin gshegs pa'i bzhugs gnas dpag tu med par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2127: na mah stree ya sogs gzungs thung yang brjod la byin gyis brlabs so //
NK004(nga)001:2128: badz+ra kha na kha na h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2130: sa gzhi rin chen sna lnga brkos pa yi /
NK004(nga)001:2131: de bzhin gshegs sku rnam dag rgyur gyur cig /
NK004(nga)001:2132: ces brjod la yid kyis kyang dmigs gzhan la'ang 'agre'o //
NK004(nga)001:2133: de nas ci tsam blang dgos pa blang la blang zin pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2134: rdo rje slob dpon gyis dkar gtor dang gser skyems 'bul tshig rgyas bsdus gang rung gis phul la /
NK004(nga)001:2137: bid+ya r+aa dza h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2138: zhes h'u bzhi pas sngags kyis phur bu bton te /
NK004(nga)001:2139: ru ru spu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+hi lo tsa ni sarba ar+tha sa d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2140: zhes sangs rgyas spyan gyis sngags bzlas te 'o ma bu gar blug /
NK004(nga)001:2141: phun sum tshogs pa dang che ba'i mchog sogs zhal
NK004(nga)001:2142: nas gsung ba'i bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa
NK004(nga)001:2143: brjod la dge legs su bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2144: de nas sngar gyi sa gtsang ma blang ba gnas
NK004(nga)001:2145: gtsang mar spungs la byin gyis brlab par bya ste
NK004(nga)001:2146: / spyir dang po a ko ta'i sngags kyis brdung /
NK004(nga)001:2147: a mri ta'i sngags kyis 'jim pa sbru /
NK004(nga)001:2148: pra mrda'i sngags kyis bardzisa la slar rnam snang gzungs ring gis byin gyis brlabs par gsung kyang /
NK004(nga)001:2149: s+aats+tsha khri 'bum sogs stabs gcig tu mang po 'debs
NK004(nga)001:2150: pa'i tshe 'jug pa mi bde bas 'di ltar bya
NK004(nga)001:2152: sa gtsang ma rnams gnas gcig tu spung ba'i mdun
NK004(nga)001:2153: rdo rje slob dpon gyis bdag bskyed rgyas par bya
NK004(nga)001:2157: rang nyid skad cig gis thub pa'i dbang po'i skur gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2159: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2161: rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya bcas tho bas brdung tshul byas la /
NK004(nga)001:2162: badz+ra murga ra +aa ko ta ya +aa ko ta ya h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2164: nyon mongs bag chags byang zhing 'jom gyur cig /
NK004(nga)001:2165: chu gtsang dri zhim spos dang sbyar ba la rdo rje'i phyag rgya gtug ste /
NK004(nga)001:2166: spos chu'i steng du a las zla dkyil las /
NK004(nga)001:2167: 'od 'phros spos chu bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2169: lan bdun gyis byin gyis brlab pas /
NK004(nga)001:2171: badz+ra pra mrda n+aa ya h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2172: ces dang rten snying bzlas la /
NK004(nga)001:2173: 'jim pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i skur gyur cig /
NK004(nga)001:2174: de nas 'jim pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK004(nga)001:2175: shud+d+he na du sho d+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2176: pad zlar 'jim pa rin chen phung por gyur //
NK004(nga)001:2177: rang gi thugs ka'i 'od zer 'og min du //
NK004(nga)001:2178: 'phros pas rnam par snang mdzad thugs rgyud bskul //
NK004(nga)001:2179: de las 'phros 'gro rgyud nyon mongs sbyangs //
NK004(nga)001:2180: slar 'dus 'jim pa'i phung po la thim pas //
NK004(nga)001:2181: bde gshegs kun gyi ye shes rang bzhin gyur //
NK004(nga)001:2182: lag g.yon pa'i mathe'u chung mthe bo'i mnan te sor
NK004(nga)001:2183: mo gsum nas re tsam kha phye ste bzhag pa
NK004(nga)001:2184: gyen bstan dang / lag g.yas kyang de bzhin byas
NK004(nga)001:2185: la kha sbub pa'i bar du 'jim pa bzhag ste
NK004(nga)001:2186: gyen bstan dang / / na mo b+ha ga ba
NK004(nga)001:2187: te bee ro tsa na pra b+ha ra dza ya
NK004(nga)001:2188: gyen bstan dang / / / ta tha ga ta ya /
NK004(nga)001:2191: su k+sh+me su k+sh+me sa me sa ma ye /
NK004(nga)001:2197: ma h+aa te dzahni ra ku le /
NK004(nga)001:2199: sarba bud+ha a d+hish+tha na a d+hish+tha te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2201: rat+na tsi ti pam tse ye bi bi sa ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2202: ci nus bzlas te byin gyis brlabs la /
NK004(nga)001:2203: 'jim pa'i gong bu las 'od 'phros 'gro don byas /
NK004(nga)001:2204: slar 'dus rin chen sna lnga'i gong bur gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2206: de dag ni byin gyis brlab pa'i rim pa ste /
NK004(nga)001:2207: 'jim pa ma bardzisa par sa'i phung po gcig la
NK004(nga)001:2208: de dang de'i tshul dang mos pa byas pas 'thus
NK004(nga)001:2209: te / de ltar ma yin par s+aats+tsha khri 'bum gyis skam po brdung ba la don med cing /
NK004(nga)001:2210: 'jim pa thams cad stabs gcig tu bardzisa pa'ang skam du 'gro ba dang /
NK004(nga)001:2211: byin brlab lan grangs mang du byas na'ang /
NK004(nga)001:2212: nyin re byin rlabs grangs mang po dgos pas mi
NK004(nga)001:2213: lcog pa sogs lag len mi bde bas sa'i phung
NK004(nga)001:2214: po byin gyis brlab na'ang 'gal ba med pa yin
NK004(nga)001:2215: no // dngos gzhi s+aats+tsha 'debs pa'i tshul ni /
NK004(nga)001:2216: s+aats+tsha 'debs pa po rnams rab tu byung ba min
NK004(nga)001:2217: cing khyim pa yin na bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad
NK004(nga)001:2219: gang du spar ba'i gnas der gzungs mdo 'don pa
NK004(nga)001:2220: po dang bcas pa tshogs shing khrus dang gtsang sbra
NK004(nga)001:2221: dang ldan pas sangs rgyas chos dang /
NK004(nga)001:2223: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2224: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi
NK004(nga)001:2225: byin gyi rlabs shing tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK004(nga)001:2226: mnga' thang chen po las chos kyi dbyings rnam par
NK004(nga)001:2227: dag cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs kyis deng
NK004(nga)001:2228: 'dir 'khor yug gi sa gzhi 'di dag bde ba
NK004(nga)001:2229: can gyi zhing gi bkod pa lta bu phun sum
NK004(nga)001:2230: tshogs pa'i yon tan thams cad kyis rnam par brgyan
NK004(nga)001:2231: pa mdzes shing yid du 'ong ba bsam gyis mi
NK004(nga)001:2232: khyab par gyur / zhes sa gzhi byin rlabs dang /
NK004(nga)001:2239: ji snyed su dag sogs yan lag bdun pa yongs rdzogs bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2240: rgyas par ni brgyad stong sogs sher phyin gyi mdo /
NK004(nga)001:2243: 'phags pa gtsug na rin po che'i zhus pa /
NK004(nga)001:2244: dri med rnam gnyis kyis gzungs mdo rnams rgyun mi chad du klog mkhan zur pa 'jog pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2245: snying po'i gzungs ring thung gis 'dzab rgyun pa 'jog par gsungs shing /
NK004(nga)001:2246: cis kyang ma 'jom na'ang gzungs mdo gnyis dang sher snying 'don pa po med pa'i thabs med do //
NK004(nga)001:2249: badz+ra pra mrda na ya h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2250: 'jim pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i skur gyur cig /
NK004(nga)001:2253: badz+ra mud+ga ra +aa ko ta ya +aa ko ta ya h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2254: nyon mongs bag chags byang zhing 'jom gyur cig /
NK004(nga)001:2257: badz+ra a yu she s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2258: 'chi med rdo rje'i srog zung thob par shog /
NK004(nga)001:2260: badz+ro b+ha b+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2261: 'od zer 'jig rten kun khyab 'gro don byas /
NK004(nga)001:2262: slar 'dus 'bi 'bi shel sgong ltar dag pa /
NK004(nga)001:2263: ye shes rdo rje 'byung ba'i rang bzhin gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2264: bskos phor ram 'bi 'bi la snum byug la /
NK004(nga)001:2265: a ra dze bi ra dze s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2266: thabs shes zung 'jug ye shes rdul bral gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2268: badz+ra d+h+aa tu gar+b+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2270: d+harma d+ha du gar+b+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2271: chos dbyings rtag pa'i snying po rnyed par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2273: badz+ra mud+ga ra +aa ko ta ya +aa ko ta ya h'u phata /
NK004(nga)001:2274: sangs rgyas kun gyis phyag rgyas btab par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2275: de yang swats+tsha brgya rtsa tsam la nges par gzungs ring thung gnyis ka dgos shing /
NK004(nga)001:2276: khri 'bum la 'grub dka' bas gzungs thung gis chog par gsungs pas /
NK004(nga)001:2277: gzungs ma bsgril bar sbyong khrus rab gnas dang bsgril
NK004(nga)001:2278: zin pa dang slar yang sbyong khrus rab gnas bsdus
NK004(nga)001:2279: pa byas pas gzungs mgo mjug ma log par gzhug
NK004(nga)001:2282: dbyings ye gnyis med chos sku'i mchod rten ni /
NK004(nga)001:2283: 'byams klas ye shes snying po khong chud gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2286: chos kyi sku las gzugs sku grangs med byon /
NK004(nga)001:2287: 'gro don 'khor ba ji srid mdzad par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2288: mdun du me tog gi gdan la bzhugs su gsol te /
NK004(nga)001:2289: su pra tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2290: stong pa'i ngang du brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2292: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma ni sha ta dib+te
NK004(nga)001:2293: dz+wa la dz+wa la d+harma d+ha du gar+b+he s+w+aa h+aa
NK004(nga)001:2295: sras bcas rgyal ba thams cad rten 'di dang /
NK004(nga)001:2296: dbyer med ro gcig brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2297: zhes rab tu gnas par bya zhing dgong mo 'jog
NK004(nga)001:2298: pa'i tshe bzang spyod smon lam dang phun sum tshogs
NK004(nga)001:2299: pa sogs bkra shis rgyas par bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2300: de ltar nyin du 'gor gyi ring la nang snga
NK004(nga)001:2301: skyabs sems nas dgong mo bsngo smon bkra shis bar
NK004(nga)001:2302: sngar ltar ro // de nas skam thag chod pa dang kha dogs lnga'i tshon gyis na bza' gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2303: ma 'byor na thams cad la sku dkar gsol la /
NK004(nga)001:2304: d+harma d+ha tu swa b+h+aa ba bi shud+he d+harma te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2305: chos dbyings rang bzhin dri ma med pa yis /
NK004(nga)001:2306: rnam par dag pa'i don dang ldan gyur cig tshon
NK004(nga)001:2307: sna lnga'i mdog gyi ras dum gang 'byor s+aats+tsha'i dbu
NK004(nga)001:2308: la sbyar te / pra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2309: rin chen brgyan bkod sna tshogs gsol ba yis /
NK004(nga)001:2310: yon tan kun rdzogs 'gro don mdzad gyur cig /
NK004(nga)001:2311: ces brjod cing don yid la bsam mo //
NK004(nga)001:2312: de nas sa sgrub skabs su s+aats+tsha rnams dkyil 'khor du gzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK004(nga)001:2313: su pra tish+tha tu be s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2314: bdag gzhan don gnyis phun tshogs spyod gyur cig /
NK004(nga)001:2315: badz+ra pad+ma sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2316: rdo rje pad+m+aa'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2317: ces brjod bzhin bzhugs su gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2319: nam mkha' sa gzhi rgya mtsho'i 'jing thams cad /
NK004(nga)001:2320: mchod rten rnam pa mang pos gang bar gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2321: ces brjod cing don bsam mo //
NK004(nga)001:2322: de nas sa sgrub kyi cho ga rgyas 'bring bsdus
NK004(nga)001:2323: pa gang rung la 'jug cing cho ga zin te
NK004(nga)001:2324: s+aats+tsha rnams dkyil 'khor nas gzhan du gshegs pa'i tshe
NK004(nga)001:2325: / s+w+aa b+h+aa wa bi shud+he a ha ra a ha ra +aa gats+tsha /
NK004(nga)001:2326: d+harma d+ha tu gar+b+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2327: chos nyid rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i ngang /
NK004(nga)001:2328: mkha' khyab 'gro ba'i don la gshegs par bsam /
NK004(nga)001:2329: nyes pa la bzod gsol ni /
NK004(nga)001:2330: +aa k+aa sha d+ha ru gar+b+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2331: 'gom yug chag grum nyes kun bzod par gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2332: 'gro rnams dri med rgyal ba'i sku thob shog /
NK004(nga)001:2333: zhes brjod bzhin s+aats+tsha rnams dkyil 'khor las gshegs te /
NK004(nga)001:2334: slar mchod rten du bzhugs su gsol ba'i tshe sngar
NK004(nga)001:2335: s+aats+tsha dkyil 'khor du bzhugs su gsol ba'i sngags dmigs
NK004(nga)001:2337: bar rnams bye ma la dam rtsi med pas nyil na skyon che /
NK004(nga)001:2338: s+aats+tsha gdab pa'i sa nyid rdo ye med pas shin
NK004(nga)001:2339: tu legs bye ma skam pos sag pa sogs kyi
NK004(nga)001:2340: s+aats+tsha rnams dbu zhabs ma log par lag tshag dam
NK004(nga)001:2341: por bya ba ni s+aats+tsha gdab pa sogs kyi thog
NK004(nga)001:2342: mtha'i bya ba'o // gsum pa sa sgrub dkyil 'khor dang mchod pa'i dbye bsdu ni /
NK004(nga)001:2343: mkhan chen cho ga gzhung du rgyas bsdus kyi khyad par mi bzhugs kyang /
NK004(nga)001:2344: dri med 'grel pa lhan skyes rol ba'i mdzad pa bzhin rgyas bsdus gnyis gsungs pa ltar na /
NK004(nga)001:2345: dkyil 'khor gang du bya ba'i gzhir rdo rje slob dpon gyis dkar gtor gser skyems phul /
NK004(nga)001:2346: thig dang phur bu gdabs pa til yungs brab pa
NK004(nga)001:2347: gzungs thung brjod pa'i bar gong gi s+aats+tsha'i lag len
NK004(nga)001:2349: dkyil 'khor gyi steng gru bzhi pa khod snyom pa
NK004(nga)001:2350: ngos bzhir seng ge brgyad bris 'bur gang rung gi
NK004(nga)001:2351: btegs pa'i rgya tshad s+aats+tsha brgya brgyad shong ba'i tshad
NK004(nga)001:2352: la ba byung dang dri bzang tsan+dana gur gum sogs
NK004(nga)001:2353: kyis chag chag btab pa ste /
NK004(nga)001:2354: sa sgrub kyi dkyil 'khor dngos ni rgya khyon s+aats+tsha brgya brgyad kyi tshad la /
NK004(nga)001:2355: gzhal yas khang rta babs med ba'i sgo skyong gi
NK004(nga)001:2356: phyi rol du khrus bardzinga dang pad+ma 'od zer gyi
NK004(nga)001:2357: 'khor yug dang bcas pa'i thig tshon spyi ltar la
NK004(nga)001:2358: / dkyil 'khor gzhan gyi lha gnas kyi mal du
NK004(nga)001:2359: s+aats+tsha ci shong gi re mig 'dab brgyad can dang
NK004(nga)001:2360: / / de phyir 'khyams rim pa gnyis su phye
NK004(nga)001:2361: ba la 'phags pa rnams gdan 'dzom pa'i gnas ste
NK004(nga)001:2362: / / / nang ma la de bzhin gshegs pa
NK004(nga)001:2363: rnams bzhugs gdan seng ge'i khri dag gis bskor ba
NK004(nga)001:2364: / / / / phyi ma la yang nang phyogs
NK004(nga)001:2365: su byang chub sems dpa' rnams bzhugs gdan pad zla
NK004(nga)001:2367: de phyir 'phags pa rang rgyal dang nyan thos chen
NK004(nga)001:2368: po bzhugs pa'i gdan pad+ma dag gis bkang bar byas
NK004(nga)001:2370: de yang dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs bzhi nas shing ru
NK004(nga)001:2371: bzhi la stegs s+aats+tsha dpang las cung mtho ba dge
NK004(nga)001:2372: 'dun gyi grangs dang mnyam pa las gcig lhag pa
NK004(nga)001:2373: byas la / stegs 'og ma las sgrub dkyil 'khor ras bris bshams /
NK004(nga)001:2374: de steng shog gu ram ras la s+aats+tsha'i rgya khyon
NK004(nga)001:2375: la gzhal ba'i ngos rer re mig bcu bcu gdabs
NK004(nga)001:2376: / tshangs thig g.yas g.yon re mig re re ste brgya brgyad dang /
NK004(nga)001:2377: re mig re la pad+ma 'dabs brgyad re spar btab
NK004(nga)001:2378: ste tshon gyis mdzes par byas pa dge 'dun grangs
NK004(nga)001:2379: mnyam bya / dkyil 'khor gyi dbus 'phrul stegs la
NK004(nga)001:2380: lug sa ma sogs de bzhin gshegs pa'i ring bsrel
NK004(nga)001:2381: gyi snying po can bzhugs su gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2382: s+aats+tsha bzhag pa'i tshe dbus nas shar lho nub byang rim bzhin g.yas skor du dgod /
NK004(nga)001:2383: dpon slob kun gyis s+aats+tsha gdan la bzhag pa dang
NK004(nga)001:2384: cho ga zin te gshegs pa'i tshe rang rang gi
NK004(nga)001:2385: sngags gsung bzhin bzhag pa dang gshegs par bya /
NK004(nga)001:2386: de yang stegs dgu byas na gcig la dkyil 'khor che ba dang /
NK004(nga)001:2387: stegs brgyad la dge 'dun brgyad 'di tsam s+aats+tsha blang bzhag kyang stabs bde 'ong ba yin /
NK004(nga)001:2388: lding khri'i khar rim bzhin ba dan dmar po brgya
NK004(nga)001:2389: brgyad la ngos rer nyer bdun re dang rgyal mtshan
NK004(nga)001:2392: dbus su thig le sngon po la gtsug tor dri
NK004(nga)001:2393: med kyi gzungs ring gser gyis bris pa 'od lnga'i
NK004(nga)001:2394: mu khyud can / ngos bzhir mchod rten phyogs mdog gi bum sgor gzungs thung dang /
NK004(nga)001:2395: gdugs la gzungs ring bris pa'i thang ka rnams bshams pa ni dkyil 'khor bshams bkod dang /
NK004(nga)001:2396: mchod pa ni dkyil 'khor gyi drung du bzhag na s+aats+tsha blang bzhag stabs mi bde bas /
NK004(nga)001:2397: bar phyes te gnas khang gi phyogs bzhir stegs kyi
NK004(nga)001:2398: steng du dbus su ts+aa ru'i gza' ba zlum gtor
NK004(nga)001:2399: che legs dkar mngar shing thog sogs zas snas brgyan
NK004(nga)001:2400: pa dang / bkra shis rdzas rtags 'bur ma ri mor bris pa /
NK004(nga)001:2401: 'bru lnga spos lnga sogs lnga tshan lnga'i rdzas dang
NK004(nga)001:2402: me tog mar me zhal zas gtso bor gyur pa'i
NK004(nga)001:2403: s+aats+tsha brgya brgyad la nyer spyod re re bzhin brgya
NK004(nga)001:2404: brgyad gyis mchod pa'i khyad par dang /
NK004(nga)001:2405: phyogs bzhir bum pa bzhi nyer lngas gtam pa'i khar
NK004(nga)001:2406: snod kyi nang du bye ma barngosa nas dug phyung
NK004(nga)001:2407: byas pa yungs dkar dang bsres pa bzhag dkyil 'khor
NK004(nga)001:2408: gyi grwa bzhir tsan+dana a dkar shug pa si la
NK004(nga)001:2409: sogs dri bzang gi dud pa rgyun mi chad pa
NK004(nga)001:2410: dang / sgo bzhir mchod yon gyi snod bzhi bzhag pa'i nang du /
NK004(nga)001:2411: rdzas bdun dang 'o ma blug mchod yon sbreng ba'i bya ma bum chu gtsang gis bkang ba /
NK004(nga)001:2412: khrus snod me long sku phyi na bza' rgyal chen
NK004(nga)001:2413: phyogs skyongs rnam la zlum gtong gsum 'bras chan sogs
NK004(nga)001:2415: slob dpon mdun du dung zhal lam khrus bum /
NK004(nga)001:2416: yungs dkar 'thor nas rdo dril bzhag /
NK004(nga)001:2417: yang rol mo'i bye brag sogs 'du bya ba ni rgyas pa'o //
NK004(nga)001:2419: dkyil 'khor gyi thig dang phur bu gdabs pa /
NK004(nga)001:2420: gzungs dang mchod rten bris pa'i thang ka rnams mi
NK004(nga)001:2421: dgos dkyil 'khor yang sgo sogs med pa'i pad+ma'i gdan
NK004(nga)001:2422: snam bu dang bcas pas chog /
NK004(nga)001:2423: mchod pa yang stabs gang bde phyogs gcig tu bshams pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2424: ts+aa ru'i bza' ba bum pa bye snod bya ma
NK004(nga)001:2425: bum spos phor rnams re re'i chog mchod pa rnams
NK004(nga)001:2426: ci 'byor ba bshams pa rung tsam yin no //
NK004(nga)001:2427: mchod rdzas gzhan rnams bardze bar ma nus kyang kha
NK004(nga)001:2428: gso tsam re dang chu gtsang ni mi 'byor thabs
NK004(nga)001:2429: med pa'i tshar re bzhin gshegs bshams bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2430: s+aats+tsha rnams dkyil 'khor du bzhag ran pa'i tshe na
NK004(nga)001:2431: ni sku dkar sogs na bza' dang ras sna lnga'i
NK004(nga)001:2432: dbu gdugs re'ang dbang lag gro phye gang rung gis
NK004(nga)001:2433: sbyar te skam zin pa dgos pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2434: gzungs ring can gyi s+aats+tsha gtsug tor dri med kyi brgya brgyad kha dog dkar po dang /
NK004(nga)001:2435: 'od dri'i go dgu kha dogs ser po bya ba sogs sngon 'gro'i sta gon legs par bya ba'o //
NK004(nga)001:2436: bzhi pa cho ga rgyas bsdus kyi gtong tshul la rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum la /
NK004(nga)001:2438: s+aats+tsha rnams dkyil 'khor du bzhag pa'i sngags gsungs bzhin bzhag ste bzhag zin pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2442: khyim pa yin na bsnyen gnas kyi khrim bsrung /
NK004(nga)001:2443: gang ltar yang sha chang sgong btsong min pa'i dkar gsum la longs spyod /
NK004(nga)001:2444: nyon mongs pa dang gnyid le lo gnod 'tshe'i bsam sbyor thog mtha' thams cad du spang /
NK004(nga)001:2445: mchog gsum dang mchod rten phan yon la yid ches
NK004(nga)001:2446: shing dad gus dang sems can la byams snying rje
NK004(nga)001:2447: bskyed pa ni dus kun gces pa'o //
NK004(nga)001:2448: gzungs mdo 'don pa dang sngags bzla ba por gnyis zur du byung na legs /
NK004(nga)001:2449: gnyis min kyang mdo 'don pa po med pa'i thabs med do //
NK004(nga)001:2450: de ni rgyas bsdus thams cad kyi thun mong gi kun spyod lags /
NK004(nga)001:2451: cho ga rgyas pa mkhan chen zhi 'tsho'i cho ga ste /
NK004(nga)001:2452: dge 'dun grwal phyag dang tshul phyag sngon du 'gro bas gdan la 'khod /
NK004(nga)001:2453: rdo rje rnam 'joms kyi gzungs dang snying po dang
NK004(nga)001:2454: khrus bdun gyi rig pa ci 'grub bzlas pas bum
NK004(nga)001:2456: 'dus pa rnams la 'thor 'thung byas la phan yon brjod /
NK004(nga)001:2458: rjes dran thub bstod gang rung /
NK004(nga)001:2459: bdag dang 'gro sogs skyabs 'gro bcas bya /
NK004(nga)001:2460: cho ga chung ba dri med lam 'jug gis dbu nas /
NK004(nga)001:2462: tshe dpag med pa'i 'jig rten gang gyur cig ces pa'i bar brjod cing sngags rnams gsum gsum bzla /
NK004(nga)001:2467: chos thams cad nas 'god par bya bar dang /
NK004(nga)001:2471: sa gzhi rten mchod byin rlabs dang /
NK004(nga)001:2472: bden stobs brjod pa gsum gsum /
NK004(nga)001:2473: mar me dang bdugs spos mchod /
NK004(nga)001:2474: pus btsug thal sbyar me tog blang la /
NK004(nga)001:2476: byin gyis brlabs pa ci gnang /
NK004(nga)001:2478: de bzhin gshegs pa sogs nas bzhes par gsol bar chog gzhung las /
NK004(nga)001:2479: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon sogs nas ci ga nang bar mchod 'bum nas /
NK004(nga)001:2480: lha'i 'jig rten nas de lta bur gshegs par gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2482: bar mtshams rnams su rol mo dkrol me tog 'thor /
NK004(nga)001:2484: pho brang gi dkyil 'khor nas bzhugs par gyur /
NK004(nga)001:2486: ye shes tshogs kyi sogs nas /
NK004(nga)001:2489: ar+g+ham 'bul ba'i tshe phyogs bzhi'i mchod yon sbreng /
NK004(nga)001:2490: khrus kyi skabs phyogs bzhi'i bum pas so sor khrus gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2491: sku phyi na bza' phul ba rnams byas te /
NK004(nga)001:2492: a di ra na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2495: yungs dkar 'bul ba'i skabs yungs dkar 'thor /
NK004(nga)001:2500: 'greng ste phyag 'tshal ba'i gzungs gsum sngon du 'gro bas phyag 'tshal bzhin /
NK004(nga)001:2502: bcom ldan 'das mi 'khrugs pa sogs nas chos dkon mchog la phyag 'tshal ba yan dang /
NK004(nga)001:2507: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das sogs skyabs su mchi'o //
NK004(nga)001:2513: mchod sprin gzungs dang rol mo bya /
NK004(nga)001:2515: ye shes tshogs rdzogs sogs ar+g+ham 'bul ba'i bya ma
NK004(nga)001:2516: bum spos kyis bdug las thal sbyar dpral bar bzung
NK004(nga)001:2517: la phyogs bzhi'i mchod yon snod du g.yas skor du
NK004(nga)001:2518: sbreng / rgyal chen sogs mchod bstod ni /
NK004(nga)001:2521: cha gsum ltar thun mongs du byin gyi brlabs /
NK004(nga)001:2525: shar phyogs na ni sogs kyi bstod pa dang phrin las bcol /
NK004(nga)001:2526: in+t+ra ya sogs kyis phyogs skyong dang /
NK004(nga)001:2527: de ba na ga sogs kyis sde brgyad la 'bul zhing /
NK004(nga)001:2528: mchod bstod dang rol mo bya /
NK004(nga)001:2530: sdig bshags nas 'grub par smon bar yongs rdzogs /
NK004(nga)001:2532: 'phags pa'i tshogs nas de bzhin gyur cig bar brjod la lan gsum gsung pa rnams /
NK004(nga)001:2533: de nas gzungs mdo dbu nas re re bzhin tshar re bklag zin pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2535: dmigs shing bsam par gzungs ring thung brgya rtsa re bzla /
NK004(nga)001:2537: phyogs bcu dus gsum sogs nas /
NK004(nga)001:2539: dri med 'od zer dang rin chen rgyal mtshan gyi bskor ba'i gzungs bdun bdun brjod /
NK004(nga)001:2540: gzhan gzungs ring thung gnyis brjod bzhin bskor ba brgya rtsa brgyad bskor /
NK004(nga)001:2542: mchod rten bskor ba'i phan yon /
NK004(nga)001:2544: spyan ras gzigs mdo las gsungs pa rnams gang rung bklag /
NK004(nga)001:2545: 'phags pa'i tshogs dang mchod sprin gzungs kyis mchod /
NK004(nga)001:2546: 'phags pa gdan 'dzom pa sogs kyis bzod par gsol /
NK004(nga)001:2547: gshegs gsol bya ba'am bstan bzhugs bya /
NK004(nga)001:2548: bzang spyod dang phun sum tshogs pa sogs bkra shis rgyas par bya /
NK004(nga)001:2549: s+aats+tsha dkyil 'khor las gshegs pa'i sngags brjod bzhin gshegs pa ni cho ga rgyas pa'o //
NK004(nga)001:2552: bsdus pa ni blo gros mtha' yas kyi gsung dri
NK004(nga)001:2553: med lam 'jug ltar nag 'gros ma ltar lags so
NK004(nga)001:2554: // de yang rgyal chen sogs kyi gtor ma nang
NK004(nga)001:2555: nub gang yin kyang re re las mi dag shing
NK004(nga)001:2556: bstod pa bton pas rung zhing /
NK004(nga)001:2557: cho ga chung ba'i dbu'i 'byung lnga mchod rten byin
NK004(nga)001:2558: rlabs mdo sde shes grub ltar gsungs pa phan yon
NK004(nga)001:2559: che bas cho ga gsum gyi dbur sbyar ba dang
NK004(nga)001:2560: / cho ga thams cad kyi dbur rjen dran dang tshig bcad gcig bzhi thub bstod res mos dang /
NK004(nga)001:2561: mjug tu bzang spyod sogs smon lam rnam gsum res mos dang /
NK004(nga)001:2562: nyin re rgyas pa gcig dang bsdus pa ci 'gro dang /
NK004(nga)001:2563: yang na 'bring po gcig dang bsdus pa ci 'gro dang /
NK004(nga)001:2564: rgyas 'bring gnyis re re dang bsdus pa ci 'gro skabs dang bstun pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2565: mchod pa'ang 'byor ldan gyis rgya mi chung ba dang /
NK004(nga)001:2566: 'byor med la de lugs bya dgos te ma 'byor
NK004(nga)001:2567: ba la nyes pa med gsungs pas skabs phyed par
NK004(nga)001:2568: bya zhing / mdor na brnyas bcos su ma song ba bya /
NK004(nga)001:2569: der 'dus pa'i dge 'dun thams cad kyis kyang sems
NK004(nga)001:2570: nyon mongs pa'i rjes su 'brang ste kha yengs mig
NK004(nga)001:2571: yengs bcas ma yin par snyigs dus kyi rgyud pa
NK004(nga)001:2572: 'di la thugs bsam re ba zhig nas bstan 'gror
NK004(nga)001:2573: sman pa'i thugs bskyed dang bcas pa'i bka' drin mdzad
NK004(nga)001:2574: par thugs rje shin tu che'o /
NK004(nga)001:2575: 'od zer dri med kyis sgrub pa ni mi re'i s+aats+tsha go dgu re khyad par dang /
NK004(nga)001:2576: cho ga 'bring bsdus gnyis gang yin kyang tshig phrad
NK004(nga)001:2577: bsgyur ba tsam las khyad yod pa ma yin no
NK004(nga)001:2578: // gnyis pa so so'i rim pa la /
NK004(nga)001:2580: dang po gtsug tor dri med la /
NK004(nga)001:2581: dkyil 'khor thig tshon gyi rnam bzhag dkyil 'khor dang mchod pa'i bshams bkod /
NK004(nga)001:2582: dngos gzhi'i cho ga gtong tshul lo //
NK004(nga)001:2583: dang po ni dkyil 'khor rgyan dang mchod pa'i bshams
NK004(nga)001:2584: bkod rgyas pa yin na thig gdan rgya khyon khru
NK004(nga)001:2586: bsdus pa khru gang min na mchod pa mi shong /
NK004(nga)001:2587: de'i dbus rgyas pa la dkyil 'khor che chung mtho 'khor /
NK004(nga)001:2589: bsdus pa mkhyud 'khor tshad du bya ba la ras
NK004(nga)001:2590: bris sam shing yin na zhal ba legs po dang
NK004(nga)001:2591: / rdo yin na phyi brdar legs par byas pa'i
NK004(nga)001:2592: dbus su thig chen brgyad spyi ltar btab pa'i dbus
NK004(nga)001:2593: nas cha chen bcu gnyis byas pas cha gsum lha
NK004(nga)001:2595: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis btab rtsig 'dod pha gsum /
NK004(nga)001:2596: drug pa phyed gdabs phyi phyed btab pa d+r+wa phyed
NK004(nga)001:2597: shar 'dab gsum bdun brgyad dgu gsum rta bab bcu
NK004(nga)001:2598: gcig bcu pa pad+ma chos 'khor gdugs gsum /
NK004(nga)001:2599: bcu gcig pa cha phran gsum gdab pa gnyis pad+ma gcig rdo rwa /
NK004(nga)001:2601: phyi rol du mchod snam zlum bskor ba'ang 'jog dbus kyi ling tshe ni /
NK004(nga)001:2602: cha chen gsum pa'i phyi thig nang nas cha phran gcig pa'i mu khyud zlum skor bya /
NK004(nga)001:2603: tshangs thig g.yas g.yon cha chen re'i zur du cha
NK004(nga)001:2604: phran re'i thig btab pa cha chen gnyis lha gnas
NK004(nga)001:2605: re mig dang / cha phran mal du rdo rje'i gdung gi ri mo bris pa yin /
NK004(nga)001:2606: khyams phyed du bgos pas nyis rim dang /
NK004(nga)001:2609: mda' thig phyir cha chen bzhi /
NK004(nga)001:2610: tshang thig g.yas g.yon cha chen gnyis gnyis su bya /
NK004(nga)001:2611: mda' phyir cha chen bzhi re'ang cha phran bzhi bzhi byas pas bcu drug ste /
NK004(nga)001:2612: gdugs cha phran gcig 'khor lo gnyis pad+ma ri dwags gcig ste shul bcu gnyis lus /
NK004(nga)001:2613: rta bab re la cha phran re byas pas bcu gcig /
NK004(nga)001:2614: gcig lhag pa mun pa dang mun rnam gnyis la phyed re bsnan pas tshang pa'o //
NK004(nga)001:2615: tshang thig g.yas g.yon cha chen gnyis dang po phyed
NK004(nga)001:2616: gdab phyi phyed dang gnyis pa cha bzhir bgos pas
NK004(nga)001:2617: re re bzhin / snam bu dang po gser snam phyogs rer brgyad /
NK004(nga)001:2620: bzhi pa rmig pa rnams mnyam par dgu re /
NK004(nga)001:2623: brgyad pa dang bdun pa mun snam drug mun pa
NK004(nga)001:2624: mun rnam gnyis kyi mthar cha phran gcig pa'i ka
NK004(nga)001:2625: thung bri / brgyad pa shar bu /
NK004(nga)001:2627: bcu pa rmig pa rnams bdun /
NK004(nga)001:2628: bcu gcig pa mda' yab lnga yin no //
NK004(nga)001:2629: kyog po'am gu na d+ha ra ni /
NK004(nga)001:2630: snam bu dang po phyed dang drug gnyis pa gsum pa drug drug /
NK004(nga)001:2632: lnga pa la ni phyed dang bzhi /
NK004(nga)001:2633: drug pa gsum nas bcad par bya /
NK004(nga)001:2634: de nas bdun pa'i tshangs rtser reg la /
NK004(nga)001:2635: de rnams nang du phyed re'i ri mo'o //
NK004(nga)001:2636: gu na d+ha na ma byas te glang rgyab bya na /
NK004(nga)001:2637: snam bu gnyis pa'i phyi thig dang /
NK004(nga)001:2638: tshangs las gnyis phyir 'dzom pa nas /
NK004(nga)001:2639: cha phran gnyis kyis g.yas g.yon bskor /
NK004(nga)001:2640: snam bu lnga pa'i phyi thig dang /
NK004(nga)001:2641: tshangs thig 'dzom pa nas bzung steng /
NK004(nga)001:2642: cha phran gnyis kyi dbus ma bskor /
NK004(nga)001:2643: de rnams phyi ru cha phran re bskor ba'o //
NK004(nga)001:2644: sna tshogs rdo rje'i rwa ni /
NK004(nga)001:2645: snam bu lnga pa'i phyi thig dang /
NK004(nga)001:2646: tshangs thig 'dzom pa'i g.yas g.yon du /
NK004(nga)001:2647: cha phran gnyis kyi steng bzung nas /
NK004(nga)001:2648: ka rgyan rtse nas bskor bar bya /
NK004(nga)001:2649: de nas phred gsum phyi ru gcig phyin te snga ma'i tshad du bskor bar bya ba yin no //
NK004(nga)001:2657: mtshams rnams tshon ma zlos pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2658: rdo rjes gdung gi mig mang ris bri gdan sngo skya /
NK004(nga)001:2661: rtsig pa nang nas dkar ljang dmar ser sngo /
NK004(nga)001:2664: gser snam 1dang rin chen 3gong 'og 4gnyis ste gsum ni ser po /
NK004(nga)001:2665: shar bu gnyis 28dang mda' 11yab gsum ni sngon po /
NK004(nga)001:2666: rmig pa gnyis dang wa ran+ta ni mdzes tshon /
NK004(nga)001:2667: mun pa mun rnam gnyis sngon po zur gyi ka thung gnyis dmar po /
NK004(nga)001:2668: de dag la ri mo 'bri na /
NK004(nga)001:2669: gser snam rin chen gnyis la pha gu 'dra ba'i rin po che'i phra tshom /
NK004(nga)001:2670: shar bu gnyis la mchu med pa'i spyi blug mgo mjug mthur du bzlog pa lta bu /
NK004(nga)001:2671: rmig pa gnyis la pad+ma kyog po rta mig gi dbyibs can /
NK004(nga)001:2672: mun pa gnyis la ri mo mi dgos shing /
NK004(nga)001:2673: mtha'i ka thung li khris bya /
NK004(nga)001:2674: wa ran+ta la 'bol ris te gos rnying kha thi'i ri mo dang phyogs 'dra /
NK004(nga)001:2675: mda' yab pad+ma phyed pa'i dbyibs can /
NK004(nga)001:2676: rta bab kyi ka ba dang /
NK004(nga)001:2677: kyog po'i nang dang sna tshogs rdo rje'i rwa rnams phyogs mdog /
NK004(nga)001:2678: kyog po'i nang du dar gyi bla re las dar 'phan nam /
NK004(nga)001:2679: nor bu'i phreng ba dpyang ba bri /
NK004(nga)001:2680: mda' yab steng du gdugs dang rgyal mtshan ba dan 'phan rnams dang /
NK004(nga)001:2681: sgo'i g.yas g.yon la khrus rdzing dang dpag bsam gyi shing rnams bri /
NK004(nga)001:2683: dbus kyi re mig la sku'am phyag mtshan 'khor lo thig le dkar po gang rung /
NK004(nga)001:2684: mdun du sbas yum thig le dkar po /
NK004(nga)001:2685: g.yas su thig le dmar po /
NK004(nga)001:2687: shar gyi re mig la sku'am phyag mtshan rdo rje'i thig le sngon po /
NK004(nga)001:2688: lhor sku'am rin po che thig le ser po /
NK004(nga)001:2695: shar lhor thig le dkar po /
NK004(nga)001:2699: gru chad kyi shar lhor thig le dkar po /
NK004(nga)001:2703: shar phyogs snam bur thig le dkar po gnyis /
NK004(nga)001:2707: shar sgor thig le dkar po /
NK004(nga)001:2710: byang sgor ljang gu rnams lha mtshan no //
NK004(nga)001:2712: dkyil 'khor pra rtsi btang ba sogs legs par bya dgos so //
NK004(nga)001:2713: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan dang mchod pa'i bshams bkod ni /
NK004(nga)001:2714: dkyil 'khor gyi rgya khyon dang mthun pa'i sgab dkris dmar po /
NK004(nga)001:2715: steng du bla re sngon po /
NK004(nga)001:2716: zhal kheb dkyil 'khor thig tshon dang mnyam pa'i ras dkar gru bzhi /
NK004(nga)001:2717: bshams bkod rgyas pa byed na /
NK004(nga)001:2719: dar dpyang ngam 'phan rnams re re bzhin so gnyis re /
NK004(nga)001:2720: 'bring po la de rnams bcu drug re /
NK004(nga)001:2721: bsdus pa la bzhi re ste /
NK004(nga)001:2722: de rnams gos dar las bzos pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2723: rdza'i 'dzug gdan rang rang dang grangs mnyam /
NK004(nga)001:2724: ting phor li zangs sogs sam rdza las byas pa rgyas pa la lnga /
NK004(nga)001:2731: mar me zhal zas de mtshungs ste /
NK004(nga)001:2733: lan tsha'i steng rdzas bdun gyis bkang dgos te /
NK004(nga)001:2734: tsam pa ka dang ba lu'i me tog lta bu dkar po /
NK004(nga)001:2740: 'o ma ma rul ba'i chur ba rnams yin no //
NK004(nga)001:2741: zhabs bsil la lan tsha'i steng /
NK004(nga)001:2742: shun pa lnga dang 'dags rdzas rigs te /
NK004(nga)001:2746: 'om bu rnams kyi bar shun dang tsan+da dkar po'i 'tshab rub mdzad /
NK004(nga)001:2749: 'bras spu bcad pa'i shun pa'i phye ma rnams blugs pa yin /
NK004(nga)001:2750: me tog 'byor na gos chen sogs las bzos pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2751: tsam pa ka'i me tog ma 'byor na 'bru dkar blug /
NK004(nga)001:2752: me tog gos chen las zos pa dang tsam pa
NK004(nga)001:2753: ka yod na 'dzug gdan me tog grangs mnyam bca'
NK004(nga)001:2754: ba las ting phor grangs bcad mi dgos /
NK004(nga)001:2755: bdug spos spos ring spos rta la btsug pa /
NK004(nga)001:2756: mar me zang rag gam rdza skong du blug /
NK004(nga)001:2762: tsan+dana dkar po ste dri lnga'i phye mas bkang /
NK004(nga)001:2763: zhal zas mar zan lta bu las bzhengs pa yin no //
NK004(nga)001:2765: dkyil 'khor gyi mthar dri dang snum bsres pas byug la legs par bshams /
NK004(nga)001:2766: log rnams sgab dkris kyi bskor /
NK004(nga)001:2767: steng du bla bre sngon po phub /
NK004(nga)001:2768: mthar byang shar nas brtsam te /
NK004(nga)001:2769: mtshams 'dzin me tog chu gnyis sogs nyer spyod rnams phyogs mtshams su bkod /
NK004(nga)001:2770: de'i phyir rgyas pa la shar du lhag gcig dang bcas rnams lnga tsam drug /
NK004(nga)001:2771: de bzhin phyogs gsum du cha drug re /
NK004(nga)001:2772: 'bring po la nang du spyi mchod dang shar du lhag gcig 'dra ba la /
NK004(nga)001:2773: phyogs rer rnam lnga cha gsum re /
NK004(nga)001:2774: bsdus pa la spyi mchod lhag pa gnyis 'dra ba la /
NK004(nga)001:2775: phyogs rer rnam lnga cha re yin no //
NK004(nga)001:2776: gdugs rgyal mtshan ba dan 'phan rnams ni rgyas pa la log rer re re bzhin brgyad re /
NK004(nga)001:2778: bsdus pa re re yin cing /
NK004(nga)001:2783: de dag gi bar mtshams rnams su s+aats+tsha ci shong bzhugs su gsol ba yin no //
NK004(nga)001:2784: gsum pa dngos gzhi'i cho ga gtong tshul la /
NK004(nga)001:2786: dngos gzhi'i cho ga gnyis las /
NK004(nga)001:2788: sngar dkyil 'khor ma bris pa'i gong yin na phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2789: bris zin na'ang cho ga yan lag tshang ba'i phyir gsung bar 'dod na /
NK004(nga)001:2790: rdo rje slob dpon gyi mdun mchod pa dang thig skud sogs nyer mkho 'du byas la /
NK004(nga)001:2793: gso sbyong blang la skyabs sems nas bdag bskyed kyi bsnyen mjug bar btang /
NK004(nga)001:2797: tshon lhag gi ye shes pa gshegs par btang /
NK004(nga)001:2798: dngos sta tha dad byed na 'og gi nongs bshags sogs mjug chog rnams bya /
NK004(nga)001:2799: dngos sta sbrel na bdag skyed sngar gyi des chog /
NK004(nga)001:2800: mchod pa bshams bkod tshul bzhin dang /
NK004(nga)001:2801: 'og tu dgos pa'i nyer mkho rnams 'du byas te /
NK004(nga)001:2802: dkyil 'khor bsang sbyang nas rim bzhin mchod pa'i phyag rgya rnams dang /
NK004(nga)001:2803: bstod pa'i rigs lnga'i rgya phral te bya ba sogs zhal rgyun bzhin /
NK004(nga)001:2804: gzhi bdag gtor ma'i mjug par btang /
NK004(nga)001:2806: ser sbreng rol mo bcas bskor ba gsum gsum bya /
NK004(nga)001:2807: phyogs rnams su rmi ngan 'jigs dang /
NK004(nga)001:2809: gzhan yang mdo rgyud rnams las byung ba'i bkra shis mang du brjod /
NK004(nga)001:2812: sogs kyi dngos grub gsol ba lan gsum 'di skabs
NK004(nga)001:2813: nang gis mchod pa rnams barje ba'am kha gso bya
NK004(nga)001:2815: da nang rang bzhin gyi mchod pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2816: rdzas ldan khyad par ba 'jog rung rnams slar gzhug pa yin /
NK004(nga)001:2818: de nas mchod pa byin rlabs nas rim bzhin la /
NK004(nga)001:2822: phyugs bcu na sogs kyi rten bzhugs lan gsum bya /
NK004(nga)001:2823: bdag dang 'gro ba nas bsdu rim bsngo ba bzang spyod smon lam /
NK004(nga)001:2824: bkra shis bcas rgyas par byas te dkyil 'khor gyi
NK004(nga)001:2825: sgo legs par kha chod bya zhing byi ba sogs
NK004(nga)001:2826: mi 'dzul ba'i zhal ba sogs lag tshag dam par
NK004(nga)001:2828: gnyis pa 'od zer dri med la /
NK004(nga)001:2829: dkyil 'khor thig tshon gyi rnam bzhag srog shing gzungs 'bul sogs lag len /
NK004(nga)001:2830: dkyil 'khor rgyan dang mchod pa'i bshams bkod /
NK004(nga)001:2831: dngos gzhi'i cho ga gtong tshul dang bzhi'o //
NK004(nga)001:2833: dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi rdo'am shing ngam ra sa sogs ci yin kyang skyang nul byas la /
NK004(nga)001:2834: mchod pa'i bshams bkod rgyas 'bring bsdus pa'i dbang gi
NK004(nga)001:2835: che chung gi tshad sngar ltar gyi dbus su thig
NK004(nga)001:2836: chen brgyad spyi ltar cha chen bcu gnyis sogs gong
NK004(nga)001:2837: bzhin la sgo gcig nub tu bstan pa /
NK004(nga)001:2838: mda' yab kyi steng bdugs dang rgyal mtshan ba dan 'phan dang /
NK004(nga)001:2839: phyi rol pad rdor 'od phreng rnams sngar ltar /
NK004(nga)001:2840: lha gnas kyi shar ngos nas nub tu phyogs pa'i
NK004(nga)001:2841: dbus su gdan ser po gru bzhi la gnas pa'i
NK004(nga)001:2842: pad zlar 'khor lo dkar po rtsib brgyad pa 'od
NK004(nga)001:2843: phreng dang bcas pa g.yas su gdan zlum po gnyis
NK004(nga)001:2844: su pad zlar / sgrib sel nor bu /
NK004(nga)001:2845: phyag rdor rdo rje sngon po /
NK004(nga)001:2846: g.yon du gdan zlum po'i steng pad zlar spyan ras
NK004(nga)001:2847: gzigs pad+ma ste 'das pa'i lha rnams dbu shar bstan
NK004(nga)001:2849: nub nas shar du phyogs par gdan zlum po gsum gyi steng /
NK004(nga)001:2850: phyag rdor mdun du khyab 'jug gi dung nag po /
NK004(nga)001:2851: 'khor lo'i thad du drag po'i rtse gsum /
NK004(nga)001:2852: pad+ma'i thad du tshogs bdag gi g.yung drung gru bzhi g.yas skor te /
NK004(nga)001:2853: 'jig rten pa'i mtshan ma gsum po mgo nub tu bstan pa'o //
NK004(nga)001:2854: lha 'jig rten 'das ma 'das gnyis kyi bar du
NK004(nga)001:2855: srog shing gi rtse bzhugs pa stong bar byas pa
NK004(nga)001:2861: byang nag rtsig pa nang nas dkar dmar ser ljang nag po'o //
NK004(nga)001:2863: gzhan rnams ni spyi dang mthun /
NK004(nga)001:2864: dkyil 'khor la pra rtsi sogs btang la legs par bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2865: gnyis pa srog shing gzungs 'bul sogs kyi lag len ni /
NK004(nga)001:2866: srog shing rgyu ni rab tsan+dana dkar dmar dang a ka ru lta bu dang /
NK004(nga)001:2867: tha ma'ang shug pa sogs 'bras bu can gyi shing
NK004(nga)001:2868: khong rul dang gas chag 'bu zos sogs kyi skyon
NK004(nga)001:2870: gnas ri bzang por skyes pa byung na legs shing
NK004(nga)001:2871: der gnas pa'i mi'am yul gyi bdag por dngos su
NK004(nga)001:2872: bslang ba dang / mi min la mchod gtor phul
NK004(nga)001:2873: nas gnang ba zhus te yar ngo gza' skar 'phrod
NK004(nga)001:2874: sbyor shis pa'i nyin mor gcod mkhan rigs rgyud la
NK004(nga)001:2876: shar phyogs mi nor ba'i mtshan mas btab te skam bcug pa las /
NK004(nga)001:2877: rlon pa ni dang po legs legs 'dra ba zhig
NK004(nga)001:2878: yin kyang phyis skams song dus yo 'khyog gas pa
NK004(nga)001:2880: srog shing ni sngar nas tshag byas te skam nges pa dgos /
NK004(nga)001:2881: de nas shing mkhan gso sbyong la gnas pas /
NK004(nga)001:2882: dbyibs gru bzhi rtsa rtse'i rnam pa phra sbom can
NK004(nga)001:2883: dang mchod rten che chung la gzhig pa'i ring thung
NK004(nga)001:2884: de ltar bya / srog shing gi rtse mor rnam
NK004(nga)001:2885: rgyal mchod rten dang rtsa bar rdo rje phyed pa
NK004(nga)001:2886: bri bsko gang rung byed srol snang ba med kyang
NK004(nga)001:2889: rnam rgyal gyi mchod rten gyi tshad med bzhi'i 'og rmang dge yan chad las seng khri mi dgos /
NK004(nga)001:2890: rmang dge nas nyi zla nor bu'i bar legs par brko /
NK004(nga)001:2891: nyi zla'i ngo shar phyogs la 'phrod par bya /
NK004(nga)001:2892: rtsa ba rdo rje phyed pa ni srog shing gi
NK004(nga)001:2893: gru bzhi'i zur la rdo rje'i rwa byas nas las
NK004(nga)001:2895: nges par rdo rje'i rwa gru bzhi'i ngos la 'phrod par bya dgos /
NK004(nga)001:2896: de la rtse mo'i mchod rten 'og tu khung bu gcig /
NK004(nga)001:2897: s+w+aa yig bris pa'i thad lta bu yin na lte
NK004(nga)001:2898: ba'i thad tsam du log bzhi la khung bu bzhi
NK004(nga)001:2899: / 'di srog shing phra na khung bu thod thug nas srog shing gi rgyun chad par 'gyur bas /
NK004(nga)001:2900: shar nub gnyis las lho byang gnyis mtho dman gtong nas brko dgos /
NK004(nga)001:2901: rtsa bar gzungs khung gcig brko /
NK004(nga)001:2902: brko ba'i tshe ring thung zab khyad bcas gzungs kyi shog dril la gzhal ba las /
NK004(nga)001:2904: brko zin pa dang gzungs khung rnam sa kyi sgo'ang
NK004(nga)001:2905: srog shing gi rgyu'i shing de nyid kyis kha legs
NK004(nga)001:2907: gzungs sgrub tshul bzhin zin te phul ba'i tshe lha'i nga rgyal la gnas pas smra ba bcad de /
NK004(nga)001:2908: man+d+ra d+ha tu gar+b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2909: rten snying rig pa phug ron /
NK004(nga)001:2910: sdig pa ci yang bzod pa dka' thub sogs gso sbyong dang bkra shis bzla bzhin phul dgos te /
NK004(nga)001:2911: gzungs khung rnams su dri bzang byug te /
NK004(nga)001:2912: phul tshul ni rtse mo'i gzungs khung du 'od zer
NK004(nga)001:2913: dri med kyi gzungs mdo ril po gser gyis bris
NK004(nga)001:2915: gtsug tor rnam rgyal gyi gzungs ring rnams phul /
NK004(nga)001:2916: smad cha'i gzungs khung bzhi ru /
NK004(nga)001:2917: srog shing gzungs go dgu dang sgrib sel gzungs go
NK004(nga)001:2918: dgu rnams ngos gsum nyer lnga re dang ngos gcig
NK004(nga)001:2919: nyer bzhi phul / rtsa ba'i gzungs khung ngu 'od
NK004(nga)001:2920: zer dri med kyi snying po dang rten snying rnams
NK004(nga)001:2921: nyer bzhi phul / phul / bskor ba'i gzungs go
NK004(nga)001:2922: dgu dang mchod pa'i gzungs rnams ni 'phang lo zhes
NK004(nga)001:2923: pa shing gi zlum skor gong bu zhig la dkris
NK004(nga)001:2924: nas dar gyi na bza' gsol te srog shing gi
NK004(nga)001:2925: rwa rtse'i 'og tu gzhug pa ste 'di la 'phang
NK004(nga)001:2926: lo zer zhes 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i gsungs shing /
NK004(nga)001:2927: gzhan zer lugs sna tshogs 'dug kyang 'di ltar bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2928: 'phang lo che chung dkyil 'khor gyi dbus stong pa tshad gzhal dgos lha rnams ma 'geb par bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2929: de ltar tsan+dana a dkar dri bzang shug phye sogs
NK004(nga)001:2930: kyis bar mtshams med par bkang la kha gcod pa'i
NK004(nga)001:2931: tshe / d+ha tu gar+b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:2932: zhes brjod de kha gcod 'geb par bya'o //
NK004(nga)001:2933: srog shing phra bas gzungs khung brko mi nyan pa'i rigs la /
NK004(nga)001:2934: de dang de'i thad du gzungs shog dril byas te bcing ba yin /
NK004(nga)001:2935: gzungs 'di dag rtse mo'i gzungs mdo rnam rgyal gzungs rnams ni glegs bam sor bzhi pa bya /
NK004(nga)001:2937: sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi pu la yash+ti /
NK004(nga)001:2940: b+ha ga wa te na ba na ba zhes tshan gnyis dang /
NK004(nga)001:2943: na ma na ba na ba dang /
NK004(nga)001:2944: mchod pa'i gzungs sam srog shing brtan pa'i sngags bi pu la bi ma le zhes pa gnyis te /
NK004(nga)001:2945: gzungs gong 'og 'di bzhi nges par go dgu re phul dgos la /
NK004(nga)001:2946: srog shing rtsa bar 'od dri'i snying po dang rten
NK004(nga)001:2947: snying gnyis go dgu 'bul dgos pa mdo las ma
NK004(nga)001:2948: bshad pas cha gang 'os phul bas chog /
NK004(nga)001:2949: gzungs 'di rnams mthud pa'i tshe dbang lag gam gro phye lta bu gtsang mas sbyar /
NK004(nga)001:2950: de'ang snga phyi'i yig 'bru gnyis ma 'grigs pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:2951: bar du zhal byang dang thig gi chod pa /
NK004(nga)001:2952: mtshams phye ba gcig gis gcig mnan pa sogs mi
NK004(nga)001:2953: rung bas mthud lugs zhib mo byas te dril tshag
NK004(nga)001:2954: dam du btang la na bza' gsol te dbu zhabs
NK004(nga)001:2955: mi nor ba'i mtshan ma bcas bya dgos la /
NK004(nga)001:2956: bsgril tshul rang lugs rdor smin rjes 'brang bcas kyi
NK004(nga)001:2957: gzungs gzhugs thams cad sngags ngo nang bstan du dbu
NK004(nga)001:2958: nas dril ba'i phyag bzhes yin cing /
NK004(nga)001:2959: bka' rgyud rjes 'brang bcas kyis sngags ngo nang bstan
NK004(nga)001:2960: gyis mjug nas dril ba'i phyag bzhes te sngags ngo
NK004(nga)001:2962: srog shig gzungs 'di shing bu gcig la gong 'og
NK004(nga)001:2963: gnyis byas nas dril na sbom phra legs pa yin
NK004(nga)001:2964: / rtse mo'i gzungs mdo glegs bam sor bzhi ni
NK004(nga)001:2965: leb mor srog shing nang du mi shong bas ma
NK004(nga)001:2966: 'khrul bar brtsegs te mjug nas dril te na bza'
NK004(nga)001:2968: dril kyang mi shong na gzungs dang byin rten rnams
NK004(nga)001:2969: zangs dang rdza'i ga'u lta bur bcug nas srog shing
NK004(nga)001:2970: la bcang na'ang rung ba yin /
NK004(nga)001:2971: de ltar nang gi gzungs gzhug kha chod bcad zin pa na /
NK004(nga)001:2972: legs par phyi brdar byas te srib sogs mi mngon par bya /
NK004(nga)001:2973: gang ltar yang gas chags shing srib sogs med pa
NK004(nga)001:2974: de 'dra byung na sman 'dam gyis bsrub sad bdar
NK004(nga)001:2975: legs por bya / ngos shin tu 'jam po la
NK004(nga)001:2976: tsan+dana nam mtshal dri bzang sogs yi ge bri ba'i
NK004(nga)001:2977: kha dogs dang mi zlos pa la lan lnga drug
NK004(nga)001:2978: byug re re bzhin srin bal lta bu 'jam pos
NK004(nga)001:2979: ur nan 'then bar byas pas bkra rtsi btang ba
NK004(nga)001:2980: lta bu'i 'jam sha 'od chags pa byung ba'i tshe
NK004(nga)001:2981: legs por bya / / 'bri rdzas rab gser dngul /
NK004(nga)001:2983: tha ma rgya snag gis lan war ram /
NK004(nga)001:2984: dbu can gyis chad lhag med par bri bar bya ste /
NK004(nga)001:2985: yig mkhan gso sbyong la gnas pas khrus byas te bri rgyu'i yi ge ni /
NK004(nga)001:2986: spyir sku gzugs dang mchod rten lta bu la mtshon na /
NK004(nga)001:2987: spyi bo dang bre'i thad du /
NK004(nga)001:2994: srog shing gi rtser rnam rgyal mchod rten yod na /
NK004(nga)001:2995: de'i 'og gi mdun ngos dang med na rtser //
NK004(nga)001:2997: tram rgyab tu h+r+ai g.yon du +aah bre'i thad du rig pa chen po'i sngags /
NK004(nga)001:2998: sarba bid+ya s+w+aa h+aah bum dbus sam snying khar /
NK004(nga)001:3001: srog shing gi rtser rnam rgyal mchod rten gyi bum ldir ram /
NK004(nga)001:3005: a'i 'og tu dbyangs dang gsal byed /
NK004(nga)001:3018: ya ra lawa sha sha sa hak+shah bum dbus sam
NK004(nga)001:3019: snying kha'i h'u dang a yu she'i gzungs kyi 'og
NK004(nga)001:3020: tu shar du gtsug tor rnam rgyal gyi gzungs thung
NK004(nga)001:3025: lhor gtsug gtor dri med kyi gzungs thung ni /
NK004(nga)001:3026: namastreeyad+hik+aan+ai sarbatatha ga tah+r+aidaya gar+b+he dz+waladz+wa lad+har+m+aa d+ha tu /
NK004(nga)001:3027: gar+b+hesamb+h+aarama ma+aayuh samshwad+haya samshwad+ha ya mam sarba papamsarba ta th+aag ta sa man+tosh+nishabi ma lebishud+d+hemh'umh'umh'umh'ubam sadzams+w+aah+aa /
NK004(nga)001:3028: nub tu gsang ba ring bsrel gyi gzungs thung ni /
NK004(nga)001:3029: sarbatath+aa ga t+ao sh+ni shad+hatumud+r+wanisarbaha rumh'umh'us+w+aah+aa /
NK004(nga)001:3030: byang du byang chub rgyan 'bum gyi gzungs thung ni /
NK004(nga)001:3035: de bzhi ka'i gsham du 'di dag bri ste /
NK004(nga)001:3037: 'di bod skad du bsgyur na ni /
NK004(nga)001:3038: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung /
NK004(nga)001:3039: rgyu de de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs /
NK004(nga)001:3040: de la 'gog pa gang yin pa //
NK004(nga)001:3041: dge sbyong chen po'i 'di skad gsungs /
NK004(nga)001:3043: rgyas par sangs rgyas rab bdun gso sbyong rgya bod skad gang rung ngam /
NK004(nga)001:3044: bsdu na rnam gzigs gso sbyong /
NK004(nga)001:3045: k+sh+aan+tihparamitahapadza paropat+aabish+ramanonah ces bod skad du /
NK004(nga)001:3046: bzod pa dka' thub bzod pa dam pa ni /
NK004(nga)001:3049: rab tu byung nas gzhan la gnod pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:3050: gzhan la 'tshe ba dge sbyong ma yin no //
NK004(nga)001:3054: zhes pa rnams yig rigs gsum gang rung gis chad lhag bris bsub med par bri /
NK004(nga)001:3055: rgyas par byas na phyogs ma nor bar rang rang
NK004(nga)001:3056: gi gzungs ring rnams bris na khyad par du 'phags
NK004(nga)001:3057: pa yin cing srog shing rtsa bar bri bar bya
NK004(nga)001:3058: ba yin no // de ltar mi shong ba'i mchod rten shin tu chung ngu la /
NK004(nga)001:3061: amri t+aaa yu t+aa tis+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:3064: rtsa bar su pra tish+tha badz+rayes+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)001:3065: zhes srog shing la yi ge phra mos bri /
NK004(nga)001:3066: gong gsal srog shing gi gzungs rnams mang po ma shong kyang re re ma phul thabs med /
NK004(nga)001:3067: gzungs chen sde lnga'i nye snying tsam phul te zhabs
NK004(nga)001:3068: bsdams kyang ring bsrel gyi snying po can gyi mchod
NK004(nga)001:3070: de ltar srog shing tshad ldan yi ge bcas bris zin pa dang /
NK004(nga)001:3072: ji snyed yod pa rnams phyi nas bcing ba yin te /
NK004(nga)001:3073: spyir mchod rten la gzungs chen sde lnga dang 'od
NK004(nga)001:3074: zer dri med kyi gzungs rnams la basngagasa pa las
NK004(nga)001:3075: / mdo rgyud gzhan gyi gzungs sogs med kyang chad pa'i skyon med mod /
NK004(nga)001:3076: sngar gyi dam pa rnams kyi phyag bzhes bzhin phul na /
NK004(nga)001:3077: rtse mo nas mas rim pa rgyud /
NK004(nga)001:3078: dang po bla ma brgyud pa'i mtshan sngags dang /
NK004(nga)001:3079: de nas bla med rnal 'byor spyod bya rgyud rnams rim bzhin /
NK004(nga)001:3080: deng sang gzungs spar rnams kyi ka tho zhal byang bzhin phul /
NK004(nga)001:3081: gzungs chen sde lnga ni srog shing dbus h'u yig bris pa'i thad tsam dang /
NK004(nga)001:3082: btags grol rigs ni yig bris pa'i 'og skor dang /
NK004(nga)001:3083: khyad par lha gcig jo bo'i grong khyer sgrol 'khor
NK004(nga)001:3084: ni rten dang sa phyogs gang na yod kyang grong
NK004(nga)001:3085: khyer de'i sems can gyi ngan 'gro'i sgo kheg par
NK004(nga)001:3086: gsungs pas re re ma phul thabs med dang /
NK004(nga)001:3087: chos skyong nor lha sogs ni bang mdzod nang du gzhug go //
NK004(nga)001:3088: bstan 'gror sman pa'i 'dod gsol dang dbyangs gsal rten
NK004(nga)001:3089: snying rig pa phug ron rnams ni stod smad thams
NK004(nga)001:3090: cad dang / rdor sems ni rigs rnams kun bdag
NK004(nga)001:3091: lags pas gong 'og thams cad du phul srol dang
NK004(nga)001:3092: cad dang / / zhal thang lta bu shong na
NK004(nga)001:3093: srog shing ngos dang dkyil 'khor ngos sogs su dgram
NK004(nga)001:3094: cad dang / / / ma shong na gong shing
NK004(nga)001:3095: dang bsgril shing med par byas nas g.yon nas dril
NK004(nga)001:3097: glegs bam sogs ni mdun ngos su sgam sogs kyi
NK004(nga)001:3098: nang du dbu ldeb yar btags te na bza' ser
NK004(nga)001:3099: po gsol / dri bzang sman spos sogs kyis sabs te dbu phyir bstan du bzhugs su gsol /
NK004(nga)001:3100: gzhan gzungs phul tshul gyi lag len zhib cha gzungs
NK004(nga)001:3101: 'bul rgyas pa dag las shes par bya dgos kyis
NK004(nga)001:3103: mchod rten la lhag par basngagasa pa ni ring bsrel rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK004(nga)001:3104: chos sku'i ring bsrel gzungs sde lnga ste da lta
NK004(nga)001:3105: gang na'ang spar yod pas cha brgya yan chad gang
NK004(nga)001:3106: thon dang / yung 'bru lta bu ni de bzhin
NK004(nga)001:3107: gshegs pa'i ring bsrel de dang rjes mthun tshad ldan
NK004(nga)001:3108: mkhas grub rtsod med kyi ring bsrel dang /
NK004(nga)001:3109: byang chub shing sogs sangs rgyas dang 'brel ba'i ring bsrel ni srog shing gi rtse mo dang /
NK004(nga)001:3111: sangs rgyas kyi dbu skra na bza' nyan rang byang
NK004(nga)001:3112: sems 'phags pa'i sar bzhugs pa'i dbu skra na bza'
